{"blogsEntriesData":[{"type":"contentEntries","id":"6-ways-to-stay-healthy-while-traveling","title":"6 Ways to Stay Healthy While Traveling","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/zA6KEFagKEcoHC6euuKS2oqOKNmeKb-metaaW5mb2dyYXBoaWMtMS0xMDI0eDEwMjQuanBn-.jpg","image":["df9ed81c-4691-48c2-98de-b974cb0ee499"],"description":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Traveling any time soon? Better make sure you&rsquo;re fit for the trip! After all, the last thing you want is to end up unwell during your long-planned holiday. We&rsquo;ve rounded up six handy reminders for staying healthy while on the go.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/bEREbQneQiDJsyvAhimfavdiLpGMpgvGapiquH97.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Wash your hands often, for 20 seconds.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If we could track how many times the &lsquo;Happy Birthday&rsquo; song is being sung these days, it would be topping the charts. 20 seconds (the length of the song) is the minimum time you should be washing your hands. Do it whenever you can!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/oIkhtaUaUfRXhOdB0aa3Jis9W7ugf6heeyXz39vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Always pack disinfectants.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You never know who&rsquo;s touched that doorknob or whose hands have been on that railing, so be sure to clean up often! Carry rubbing alcohol and hand sanitizer in your bag so you can disinfect regularly. Avoid touching your face too!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/BKyWc3Qqlxw4UikIpaoKNrL8Ox2Xq8ks41hfc0F9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Boost your immune system.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Your body&rsquo;s shields have to be up as you get around. Take your multivitamins regularly so you can boost your immune system. Healthy juices like orange juice are also packed with vitamin C that can help keep your body at its best.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/wwRrYsELV4GEUeYQzEOx8U9h39zaaZZWsr1b8GEJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Eat well.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Now (more than ever) is the time to go green. Pile those veggies on your plate because studies have shown greens help increase your antibody response. This fights infections and other unwanted germs that hijack your system and make you sick.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/MVY2qV9IU7eCT2te2fMqF2lurylhc64PBZOL0NSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Rest up.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Save the Netflix bingeing for tomorrow and get those eight hours of sleep. You&rsquo;re gonna need them. Staying up late makes you more likely to get sick when you&rsquo;re exposed to a virus. You don&rsquo;t want to catch a cold and have it turn into something more serious, so call it a day early enough for you to get ample rest.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/GvLs7JA31VzuTU60aN9ojy3Hx3iBjiolpuPdWOGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Get insurance.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getting sick while you&rsquo;re traveling is enough of its own headache, so do everything you can to get coverage. Having insurance that covers sicknesses that you can catch while traveling (especially more serious ones) at least puts you a little more at ease. Hopefully you won&rsquo;t need it though!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A responsible traveler puts safety first, so be sure you take all the necessary precautions as you plan your trips!</p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":[]}},"order":null,"published_at":"2020-10-11T16:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blog/6-ways-to-stay-healthy-while-traveling","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-03-05T06:16:36.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-10-21T09:39:21.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"323","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Traveling any time soon? Better make sure you&rsquo;re fit for the trip! After all, the last thing you want is to end up unwell during your long-planned holiday. We&rsquo;ve rounded up six handy reminders for staying healthy while on the go.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/bEREbQneQiDJsyvAhimfavdiLpGMpgvGapiquH97.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Wash your hands often, for 20 seconds.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If we could track how many times the &lsquo;Happy Birthday&rsquo; song is being sung these days, it would be topping the charts. 20 seconds (the length of the song) is the minimum time you should be washing your hands. Do it whenever you can!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/oIkhtaUaUfRXhOdB0aa3Jis9W7ugf6heeyXz39vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Always pack disinfectants.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You never know who&rsquo;s touched that doorknob or whose hands have been on that railing, so be sure to clean up often! Carry rubbing alcohol and hand sanitizer in your bag so you can disinfect regularly. Avoid touching your face too!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/BKyWc3Qqlxw4UikIpaoKNrL8Ox2Xq8ks41hfc0F9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Boost your immune system.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Your body&rsquo;s shields have to be up as you get around. Take your multivitamins regularly so you can boost your immune system. Healthy juices like orange juice are also packed with vitamin C that can help keep your body at its best.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/wwRrYsELV4GEUeYQzEOx8U9h39zaaZZWsr1b8GEJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Eat well.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Now (more than ever) is the time to go green. Pile those veggies on your plate because studies have shown greens help increase your antibody response. This fights infections and other unwanted germs that hijack your system and make you sick.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/MVY2qV9IU7eCT2te2fMqF2lurylhc64PBZOL0NSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Rest up.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Save the Netflix bingeing for tomorrow and get those eight hours of sleep. You&rsquo;re gonna need them. Staying up late makes you more likely to get sick when you&rsquo;re exposed to a virus. You don&rsquo;t want to catch a cold and have it turn into something more serious, so call it a day early enough for you to get ample rest.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/GvLs7JA31VzuTU60aN9ojy3Hx3iBjiolpuPdWOGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Get insurance.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getting sick while you&rsquo;re traveling is enough of its own headache, so do everything you can to get coverage. Having insurance that covers sicknesses that you can catch while traveling (especially more serious ones) at least puts you a little more at ease. Hopefully you won&rsquo;t need it though!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A responsible traveler puts safety first, so be sure you take all the necessary precautions as you plan your trips!</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"324","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"[]","state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"1788","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"zA6KEFagKEcoHC6euuKS2oqOKNmeKb-metaaW5mb2dyYXBoaWMtMS0xMDI0eDEwMjQuanBn-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"9981","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}},{"id":"28261","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"zA6KEFagKEcoHC6euuKS2oqOKNmeKb-metaaW5mb2dyYXBoaWMtMS0xMDI0eDEwMjQuanBn-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"28262","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":["df9ed81c-4691-48c2-98de-b974cb0ee499"],"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"28263","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Traveling any time soon? Better make sure you&rsquo;re fit for the trip! After all, the last thing you want is to end up unwell during your long-planned holiday. We&rsquo;ve rounded up six handy reminders for staying healthy while on the go.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/bEREbQneQiDJsyvAhimfavdiLpGMpgvGapiquH97.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Wash your hands often, for 20 seconds.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If we could track how many times the &lsquo;Happy Birthday&rsquo; song is being sung these days, it would be topping the charts. 20 seconds (the length of the song) is the minimum time you should be washing your hands. Do it whenever you can!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/oIkhtaUaUfRXhOdB0aa3Jis9W7ugf6heeyXz39vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Always pack disinfectants.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You never know who&rsquo;s touched that doorknob or whose hands have been on that railing, so be sure to clean up often! Carry rubbing alcohol and hand sanitizer in your bag so you can disinfect regularly. Avoid touching your face too!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/BKyWc3Qqlxw4UikIpaoKNrL8Ox2Xq8ks41hfc0F9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Boost your immune system.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Your body&rsquo;s shields have to be up as you get around. Take your multivitamins regularly so you can boost your immune system. Healthy juices like orange juice are also packed with vitamin C that can help keep your body at its best.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/wwRrYsELV4GEUeYQzEOx8U9h39zaaZZWsr1b8GEJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Eat well.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Now (more than ever) is the time to go green. Pile those veggies on your plate because studies have shown greens help increase your antibody response. This fights infections and other unwanted germs that hijack your system and make you sick.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/MVY2qV9IU7eCT2te2fMqF2lurylhc64PBZOL0NSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Rest up.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Save the Netflix bingeing for tomorrow and get those eight hours of sleep. You&rsquo;re gonna need them. Staying up late makes you more likely to get sick when you&rsquo;re exposed to a virus. You don&rsquo;t want to catch a cold and have it turn into something more serious, so call it a day early enough for you to get ample rest.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/GvLs7JA31VzuTU60aN9ojy3Hx3iBjiolpuPdWOGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Get insurance.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getting sick while you&rsquo;re traveling is enough of its own headache, so do everything you can to get coverage. Having insurance that covers sicknesses that you can catch while traveling (especially more serious ones) at least puts you a little more at ease. Hopefully you won&rsquo;t need it though!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A responsible traveler puts safety first, so be sure you take all the necessary precautions as you plan your trips!</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"28264","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}},{"id":"28265","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":[],"state_path":"main.gallery_images","type":"file"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"tips-for-a-happysummer","title":"Tips for a #HappySummer","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/fnsyQq08aj79mOekfH0vReiVGKl7Dc-metaU2NyZWVuc2hvdCAyMDI0LTA2LTE0IDE2NTQ0OS5qcGc%3D-.jpg","image":["0bd36b42-e3da-4401-a0e3-1df9bd8efe91"],"description":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Start packing your bags because summer is here! Whether you plan on going camping, hiking, or swimming at the beach here are some things you&rsquo;ll need to bring with you can enjoy your vacation to the max while being eco-friendly!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Here are the <strong>Top 5</strong> ways you can have fun while healing Mother Earth.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/8IUW4PBN5eExX6JGMoZqPSv8vLyiKD0EWZli54Yw.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Going for a swim? Use a reef-safe sunscreen or wear a rashguard.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">It&rsquo;s important to protect yourself from the sun&rsquo;s harsh UV rays and it&rsquo;s just as important to protect our marine life from harsh chemicals. No sunscreen is 100% safe but there are some brands that don&rsquo;t use oxybenzone and octinoxate in their sunscreen which makes them more environment-friendly.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/4O7xRc5O7sJSDG9lLEwEdtA8WPM6WwAzcVoGzMSp.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Bring a water thermos to keep your cool for longer.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">When travelling with a group, most people don&rsquo;t finish the water from plastic bottles because:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">1.) They don&rsquo;t know which bottle is theirs or,</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">2.) The plastic has been exposed to the sun making the water unsafe to drink.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Decrease plastic waste by bringing your own personal water thermos wherever you go to keep your water refreshingly cool and safe to drink.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/9q3aK4KCLDl1yF4ixbXIVHBwSCG93nPSynbGi39J.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Pack your tote bags for your souvenir shopping.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Souvenir shopping is one of the highlights for these trips and we can&rsquo;t help but buy at almost every shop. Instead of asking for a plastic bag for your trinkets, bring your own bag to store your haul. After all, carrying multiple different colored plastic bags will not only ruin your style, but it&rsquo;s also hazardous for the environment.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/z44hHfCfyE7ollwP54W7pVO0KACeNDy4PORQj8aN.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Be a conscious consumer when buying souvenirs.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Supporting the local businesses is much appreciated but make sure that the items you&rsquo;re buying did not harm any living creatures or cause damage to their eco-system. After all, this might just be a tourist spot to you, but these places are homes to others.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/sIenHKycLW0jb5ukZkD9wrp74zOFBfvGODh6tk1O.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Shampoo bars are better for your and the environment.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Shampoo bars are usually made with essential oils that are good for your hair and come in eco-friendly packaging to save yourself from the hassle of opening &amp; keeping those messy, non-biodegradable sachets.</p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2023-03-11T16:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blog/tips-for-an-eco-friendly-happy-summer","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-03-12T02:14:48.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-07-19T02:12:45.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"585","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"fnsyQq08aj79mOekfH0vReiVGKl7Dc-metaU2NyZWVuc2hvdCAyMDI0LTA2LTE0IDE2NTQ0OS5qcGc=-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"586","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"[\"0bd36b42-e3da-4401-a0e3-1df9bd8efe91\"]","state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[{"id":"719","type":"media","attributes":{"uuid":"0bd36b42-e3da-4401-a0e3-1df9bd8efe91","collection_name":"blueprint_media","file_name":"tgUkpvjDC6xPUXAsNMwPfiwxOJWpf0-metaU2NyZWVuc2hvdCAyMDI0LTA2LTE0IDE2NTQ0OS5qcGc=-.jpg","custom_properties":[],"original_url":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/719/tgUkpvjDC6xPUXAsNMwPfiwxOJWpf0-metaU2NyZWVuc2hvdCAyMDI0LTA2LTE0IDE2NTQ0OS5qcGc%3D-.jpg","generated_conversions":{"blog_show":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/719/conversions/tgUkpvjDC6xPUXAsNMwPfiwxOJWpf0-metaU2NyZWVuc2hvdCAyMDI0LTA2LTE0IDE2NTQ0OS5qcGc%3D--blog_show.jpg"},"type":"image"}}]}},{"id":"587","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<h2>Going for a swim? Use a reef-safe sunscreen or wear a rashguard</h2>\n<p>It&rsquo;s important to protect yourself from the sun&rsquo;s harsh UV rays and it&rsquo;s just as important to protect our marine life from harsh chemicals. No sunscreen is 100% safe but there are some brands that don&rsquo;t use oxybenzone and octinoxate in their sunscreen which makes them more environment-friendly.</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9974","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"fnsyQq08aj79mOekfH0vReiVGKl7Dc-metaU2NyZWVuc2hvdCAyMDI0LTA2LTE0IDE2NTQ0OS5qcGc=-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"9975","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":["0bd36b42-e3da-4401-a0e3-1df9bd8efe91"],"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"9976","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Start packing your bags because summer is here! Whether you plan on going camping, hiking, or swimming at the beach here are some things you&rsquo;ll need to bring with you can enjoy your vacation to the max while being eco-friendly!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Here are the <strong>Top 5</strong> ways you can have fun while healing Mother Earth.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/8IUW4PBN5eExX6JGMoZqPSv8vLyiKD0EWZli54Yw.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Going for a swim? Use a reef-safe sunscreen or wear a rashguard.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">It&rsquo;s important to protect yourself from the sun&rsquo;s harsh UV rays and it&rsquo;s just as important to protect our marine life from harsh chemicals. No sunscreen is 100% safe but there are some brands that don&rsquo;t use oxybenzone and octinoxate in their sunscreen which makes them more environment-friendly.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/4O7xRc5O7sJSDG9lLEwEdtA8WPM6WwAzcVoGzMSp.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Bring a water thermos to keep your cool for longer.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">When travelling with a group, most people don&rsquo;t finish the water from plastic bottles because:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">1.) They don&rsquo;t know which bottle is theirs or,</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">2.) The plastic has been exposed to the sun making the water unsafe to drink.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Decrease plastic waste by bringing your own personal water thermos wherever you go to keep your water refreshingly cool and safe to drink.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/9q3aK4KCLDl1yF4ixbXIVHBwSCG93nPSynbGi39J.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Pack your tote bags for your souvenir shopping.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Souvenir shopping is one of the highlights for these trips and we can&rsquo;t help but buy at almost every shop. Instead of asking for a plastic bag for your trinkets, bring your own bag to store your haul. After all, carrying multiple different colored plastic bags will not only ruin your style, but it&rsquo;s also hazardous for the environment.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/z44hHfCfyE7ollwP54W7pVO0KACeNDy4PORQj8aN.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Be a conscious consumer when buying souvenirs.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Supporting the local businesses is much appreciated but make sure that the items you&rsquo;re buying did not harm any living creatures or cause damage to their eco-system. After all, this might just be a tourist spot to you, but these places are homes to others.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/sIenHKycLW0jb5ukZkD9wrp74zOFBfvGODh6tk1O.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Shampoo bars are better for your and the environment.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Shampoo bars are usually made with essential oils that are good for your hair and come in eco-friendly packaging to save yourself from the hassle of opening &amp; keeping those messy, non-biodegradable sachets.</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9977","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"your-guide-to-a-seamless-travel-experience","title":"Your Guide to a Seamless Travel Experience","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tKG5KgegcpCz0eFTpcApYsd530Zv4s-metaSXNsYW5kIEhvcHBpbmctMS5qcGc%3D-.jpg","image":["971140de-decc-48c8-9429-7024f4f5bc38"],"description":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Whether it&rsquo;s a solo travel adventure, a romantic retreat, or a <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/special-offers/savings-on-spacious-suites\">family getaway</a>, nothing beats the bubbling excitement of an upcoming trip! While navigating unfamiliar destinations can sometimes leave you feeling overwhelmed, don&rsquo;t worry! With the right mindset and preparation, you&rsquo;re on your way to a seamless travel experience.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Join us as we explore essential tips to help you make the most of your trip.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Research your destination</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/jl3lMTa5yOy3SwWykwFrmysB7aH0OsrWVphVPplV.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Familiarity with your chosen destination is the first step to making the most of your trip. For instance, having a background in the local culture will also give you an idea of what attractions to visit, activities to try, and signature dishes to feast on.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Moreover, being aware of the destination&rsquo;s customs and traditions will also help in raising awareness about the specific destination&rsquo;s proper etiquette, including what to wear and how to behave in public. On <a href=\"https://www.discoveryshoresboracay.com/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">Boracay Island</a>, wearing light clothing over swimwear when entering establishments is highly advised as a sign of respect for the island&rsquo;s culture.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Create a flexible itinerary</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0Ka81jHW0119GWLdwhNmkgVd1r5u8HNYJCJW5LYO.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">While being spontaneous has its perks, having an outline of your travel plans, such as including your transportation, accommodation, and activities, can help transition you to a smooth sailing journey. It&rsquo;s best to keep your travel itinerary flexible; it does not have to be something that you have to follow strictly. This will allow you to have more fun than worrying about following your schedule.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Maximize your time</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/rO7Yia5zEth90TJnitn5Mq2eLYOpoK1zf5lK1fN0.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A seamless travel experience includes maximizing your time. This will enable you to achieve a full travel experience as you immerse yourself in the destination&rsquo;s culture, attractions, and activities. Despite the limited number of days during a vacation, the efficient use of your time can enhance the overall quality of your travel experience. This is the perfect chance to fulfill your travel aspirations as you tick off some items from your bucket list.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Explore your accommodation options with Discovery hotels and resorts</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choosing the right accommodation greatly matters while you are on vacation. It&rsquo;s important to find comfort and ease as you relax after a long day of excursions and thrilling activities. Deeply rooted in providing a &ldquo;Service That&rsquo;s All Heart,&rdquo; Discovery hotels and resorts are ready to welcome you to a home away from home. Whether you are seeking a <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/philippines-hotels-resorts-discovery-resorts\">breathtaking beach destination</a> in the Philippines or a vibrant urban oasis, each property is meticulously designed for every discerning traveler.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Have a look at your guide below:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Wy2qV2vfLjCm7GXhspMhaCpINOXQ6iTFzZNSb3s6.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"2225\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.9691px;\">You can make the most of your seamless travel experience with a touch of&nbsp; &lsquo;Service That&rsquo;s All Heart&rsquo; with Discovery hotels and resorts. For more information, visit our website at <a href=\"../../../../../\">www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com</a></span></span></p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2024-01-30T16:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blog/your-guide-to-a-seamless-travel-experience","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-05-07T03:45:37.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-10-01T03:35:53.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"5825","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"tKG5KgegcpCz0eFTpcApYsd530Zv4s-metaSXNsYW5kIEhvcHBpbmctMS5qcGc=-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"5826","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"[\"971140de-decc-48c8-9429-7024f4f5bc38\"]","state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[{"id":"845","type":"media","attributes":{"uuid":"971140de-decc-48c8-9429-7024f4f5bc38","collection_name":"blueprint_media","file_name":"2bAau0uxqiA4TFbEneNWik5vADZERW-metaSXNsYW5kIEhvcHBpbmctMS5qcGc=-.jpg","custom_properties":[],"original_url":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/845/2bAau0uxqiA4TFbEneNWik5vADZERW-metaSXNsYW5kIEhvcHBpbmctMS5qcGc%3D-.jpg","generated_conversions":{"blog_show":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/845/conversions/2bAau0uxqiA4TFbEneNWik5vADZERW-metaSXNsYW5kIEhvcHBpbmctMS5qcGc%3D--blog_show.jpg"},"type":"image"}}]}},{"id":"5827"