tyle=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Research your destination</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/jl3lMTa5yOy3SwWykwFrmysB7aH0OsrWVphVPplV.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Familiarity with your chosen destination is the first step to making the most of your trip. For instance, having a background in the local culture will also give you an idea of what attractions to visit, activities to try, and signature dishes to feast on.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, being aware of the destination&rsquo;s customs and traditions will also help in raising awareness about the specific destination&rsquo;s proper etiquette, including what to wear and how to behave in public. For example, on Boracay Island, wearing light clothing over swimwear when entering establishments is highly advised as a sign of respect for the island&rsquo;s culture.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Create a flexible itinerary</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0Ka81jHW0119GWLdwhNmkgVd1r5u8HNYJCJW5LYO.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">While being spontaneous has its perks, having an outline of your travel plans, such as including your transportation, accommodation, and activities, can help transition you to a smooth sailing journey. It&rsquo;s best to keep your travel itinerary flexible; it does not have to be something that you have to follow strictly. This will allow you to have more fun than worrying about following your schedule.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Maximize your time</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/rO7Yia5zEth90TJnitn5Mq2eLYOpoK1zf5lK1fN0.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A seamless travel experience includes maximizing your time. This will enable you to achieve a full travel experience as you immerse yourself in the destination&rsquo;s culture, attractions, and activities. Despite the limited number of days during a vacation, the efficient use of your time can enhance the overall quality of your travel experience. This is the perfect chance to fulfill your travel aspirations as you tick off some items from your bucket list.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Explore your accommodation options with Discovery hotels and resorts</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Choosing the right accommodation greatly matters while you are on vacation. It&rsquo;s important to find comfort and ease as you relax after a long day of excursions and thrilling activities. Deeply rooted in providing a &ldquo;Service That&rsquo;s All Heart,&rdquo; Discovery hotels and resorts are ready to welcome you to a home away from home. Whether you are seeking a breathtaking beach destination or a vibrant urban oasis, each property is meticulously designed for every discerning traveler.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Have a look at your guide below:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Wy2qV2vfLjCm7GXhspMhaCpINOXQ6iTFzZNSb3s6.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"2225\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.9691px;\">You can make the most of your seamless travel experience with a touch of&nbsp; &lsquo;Service That&rsquo;s All Heart&rsquo; with Discovery hotels and resorts. For more information, visit our website at <a href=\"../../../../../\">www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com</a></span></span></p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9973","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"discovery-hospitality-corporation-crowned-as-the-leading-hospitality-brand-in-the-philippines","title":"Discovery Hospitality Corporation, Crowned as the Leading Hospitality Brand in the Philippines","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/UUw4cfDQ1Upo9wGkc2aj0j8S96YNdY-metaREhDcy1Kb3NlLVBhcnJlbm8tSnItYXMtQ09PLW9mLXRoZS1ZZWFyLWluLUhvc3BpdGFsaXR5LWFuZC1CbGVzc3ktVG93bmVzLWFzLUhvdGVsLURpZ2l0YWwtTWFya2V0aW5nLUxlYWRlci1mb3ItQVBBQy0yMDQ4eDEzNjUgKDEpLmpwZw%3D%3D-.jpg","image":["0418363d-ffa2-4cfc-927d-022f41b5d2a6"],"description":"<p>Discovery Hospitality Corporation (DHC) proudly added three more awards to its collection this year after receiving three recognitions at the World Business Outlook Awards 2023 held last November 25 at the Marriott Marquis in Bangkok, Thailand.</p>\n<p>The World Business Outlook Awards is a prestigious event led by Singapore-based global media publication, World Business Outlook, featuring industry business updates and providing a global voice and perspective to open conversations that are game-changers. To continue its mission of delivering information with legitimacy standards, this award-giving event recognizes excellence in different industries, applauding both individuals and organizations for their remarkable performance and innovative contributions. These awards highlight top-tier business professionals and industry leaders across the globe.</p>\n<p>This event acknowledged the outstanding achievements of DHC as this year&rsquo;s &lsquo;Leading Hospitality Brand in the Philippines&rsquo;. Additionally, Ms. Blessy Townes, Vice President and Head of Digital Marketing and Branding, was honored as &lsquo;Hospitality Digital Marketing Leader of the Year in the APAC region&rsquo;. And with heartfelt delight, Mr. Jose Parre&ntilde;o, Jr., Chief Operating Officer of Discovery Hospitality Corporation, was presented with the esteemed title of &lsquo;COO of the Year in the Hospitality Sector of the Philippines.&rsquo;</p>\n<p>Discovery Hospitality Corporation is a proud homegrown brand managing the Philippines&rsquo; <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/select-by-hotel\">best-loved hotels and resorts</a>, namely Discovery Shores Boracay, Club Paradise Palawan, Discovery Suites, and Discovery Primea. Just this year, it opened two new properties: Manami Resort under its new brand called Signature Collection, and Discovery Samal, the first property to highlight the rebranded Discovery Resorts. From purely heading and operating these owned properties, DHC has trailblazed and expanded its horizons to more than just focusing on its own but also sharing its expertise from decades of experience to provide allied and <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/shared-services\">shared services</a> and property management with other businesses, all while continuing to lead its legacy onwards and upwards.</p>\n<p>For Parre&ntilde;o, each award attributed to DHC serves as a reaffirmation of Discovery&rsquo;s goal of achieving excellence. &ldquo;We take pride in the continuous recognition from The World Business Outlook. These accolades not only inspire us but also serve as a reminder to consistently raise the standards in the hospitality field. Through continuous innovation, our aim is always to provide &ldquo;Service That&rsquo;s All Heart&rdquo; to each and every guest,&rdquo; added Parre&ntilde;o.</p>\n<p>To DHC&rsquo;s management team, these awards reflect their collective passion and dedication, as well as the exceptional leadership of Parre&ntilde;o and Townes. Every recognition, according to Parre&ntilde;o, &ldquo;reflects the success of Discovery&rsquo;s efforts and the unforgettable experience we impart on our guests.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;Over the years, the definition of luxury travel hasn&rsquo;t been merely a destination, but now the shift has moved into creating memorable and authentic experiences. By valuing each guest, we ensure they relish every moment of their stay with us, which in turn produces unparalleled service,&rdquo; Parre&ntilde;o concluded.</p>\n<p>Discovery Hospitality Corporation continues to solidify its brand love and remarkable connections to its guest, business partners, and internal stakeholders. It strives to deliver authentic experiences that are true to the locale and build hotel brands that inspire the modern traveler, underpinned by genuine Filipino warmth.</p>\n<p>For inquiries on <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/hotel-management-company\">hotel management</a> and digital shared services, contact DHC&rsquo;s Senior Vice President and Head of Sales and Operations, Lynette Ermac, at <a href=\"mailto:cathy.nepomuceno@discoveryhospitality.com\">lynette.ermac@discoveryhospitality.com</a>. For more information, visit <a href=\"../../../../\">www.discoveryhospitality.com</a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PRESS</h3>\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; ; gap: 20px;\">\n<p><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/6mcsYJuYVSw3gESW3fUHmEXLkHCEA9KsfBOyYRtC.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"367\" height=\"367\" /></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px; background-color: #fffff