thy involves sweating it out too. Download a fitness app, watch workout videos online, or even sign up for the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yogaplusph/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">livestream classes</a> that some studios offer!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/sUvc6itPllj0Fiuad9AAAYwkvftHzbtJOYMqJyss.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Put on your thinking cap.</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.9691px;\">Staying indoors shouldn&rsquo;t keep you from flexing those brain muscles. Learn a new <a href=\"https://www.timeout.com/los-angeles/news/gucci-osterias-massimo-bottura-is-offering-free-virtual-cooking-classes-on-instagram-031620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">skill</a> or sign up for an online <a href=\"https://www.yugatech.com/guides/free-online-courses-to-take-during-the-one-month-quarantine/?fbclid=IwAR1LDq7cjZli_8Wyr8OXOKfkqf3fhjfA0bGxRjh7S5EOfGLeAhV3pDc31BM#sthash.tc7FaAW4.dpbs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">class</a>! There are plenty of free workshops and other resources you can look into that will certify you in a field of expertise over the course of a few weeks.</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/GzZXcVgqwqG8IkhcB7NaMGgd9OcVIPmA7jNIbXyV.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Start planning your next trip.</strong></p>\n<p>You don&rsquo;t have to wait another month before setting things in motion for your dream destination! Pristine beaches in <a href=\"https://discoveryshoresboracay.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Boracay</a> and <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Coron</a> are going to be perfect for filling in your wanderlust gap. Try looking at a possible itinerary too so you can prepare arrangements for activities and know who to call as soon as you can. And of course, Discovery Shores Boracay and Club Paradise Palawan will be waiting to welcome you warmly for your summer holiday.</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9982","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"otbjTv6RLriLi0df9o1lfoj2xhkBE0-metaMS0xMDI0eDEwMjQuanBn-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"9983","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":["4010bb69-6700-4fbd-ba59-784840de3c1a"],"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"9984","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Summer is finally here, and though we can&rsquo;t go rushing to the beach just yet, there&rsquo;s plenty to keep us busy in the great indoors. We&rsquo;ve rounded up 9 activities you can enjoy whether you&rsquo;re safely checked in or staying cozy at home.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/3XrMSaiCX0PIgh2Q6VB6AZLBM1Fw9bV1ahKpUmK6.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Dig into your movie bucket list.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Oscar nominees, foreign language must-sees, old Hollywood classics, that documentary on global warming. We all have films we keep saying we&rsquo;re going to watch but have never actually sat through. Now&rsquo;s the perfect time to dust off those DVDs or clear out your Watch List. You might even pick up some travel inspo from what you <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100068016172309/posts/2913677768715338/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">watch</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.9691px;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/4wuXmv6mArLePi77iVw97MBZ6gCgiP4rcILsaGFc.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Settle in with a good read.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Remember all those books you hoarded at the fair, posted on your Instagram stories, and immediately dumped on your bedside table? Time to pull a good read off the shelf! Or if you&rsquo;re looking for something to listen to while cleaning up or cooking, <a href=\"https://www.audible.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">audiobooks</a> are a great way to multitask.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14.9691px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.9691px;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/nzvzEiKTG1t5jSSSpfInlvNW0dJpgZXB2jkogGLC.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Try a new recipe.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Speaking of cooking, it&rsquo;s time to contend with your market haul (shop responsibly, folks!) Look for inspiration from online <a href=\"https://www.bonappetit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">food magazines</a>, YouTube channels, even your favorite celebrities firing up their stoves and keeping their kitchens busy. Besides, you&rsquo;re going to get tired of the same pasta recipe at some point.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/b08ras9zXukgQXgr34YmTx7rJZ5ko5aWxhraA4ZM.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Get moving.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Can&rsquo;t go outdoors? Not an excuse to not exercise. Staying healthy involves sweating it out too. Download a fitness app, watch workout videos online, or even sign up for the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yogaplusph/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">livestream classes</a> that some studios offer!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/sUvc6itPllj0Fiuad9AAAYwkvftHzbtJOYMqJyss.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Put on your thinking cap.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Staying indoors shouldn&rsquo;t keep you from flexing those brain muscles. Learn a new <a href=\"https://www.timeout.com/los-angeles/news/gucci-osterias-massimo-bottura-is-offering-free-virtual-cooking-classes-on-instagram-031620\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">skill</a> or sign up for an online <a href=\"https://www.yugatech.com/guides/free-online-courses-to-take-during-the-one-month-quarantine/?fbclid=IwAR1LDq7cjZli_8Wyr8OXOKfkqf3fhjfA0bGxRjh7S5EOfGLeAhV3pDc31BM#sthash.tc7FaAW4.dpbs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">class</a>! There are plenty of free workshops and other resources you can look into that will certify you in a field of expertise over the course of a few weeks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/GzZXcVgqwqG8IkhcB7NaMGgd9OcVIPmA7jNIbXyV.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Start planning your next trip.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You don&rsquo;t have to wait another month before setting things in motion for your dream destination! Pristine beaches in <a href=\"https://discoveryshoresboracay.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Boracay</a> and <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Coron</a> are going to be perfect for filling in your wanderlust gap. Try looking at a possible itinerary too so you can prepare arrangements for activities and know who to call as soon as you can. And of course, Discovery Shores Boracay and Club Paradise Palawan will be waiting to welcome you warmly for your summer holiday.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/nJ1n4p8MOBOIWmDC9aKDq8lPxBZ75VHmEWH52MTI.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Go on virtual tours.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You don&rsquo;t have to hop on a plane to get your culture fix! <a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/what-to-do-at-home-streaming-art-museums-concerts-coronavirus-trnd/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Museums</a> all over the world are opening their virtual doors so you can still enjoy exhibits right from your couch. You can also check out plays and concerts streaming online for free!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/ehWytmczSGzpdjFfYYkfkV3Yka2cCrZRMyEDDLwc.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Start a new passion project.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;ve always wanted to try your hand at painting or have been keeping that screenplay idea in your notes for years, now&rsquo;s the perfect time to jump on those! Let those creative juices flow and stop feeling bad about never acting on that passion project. Tend to your garden, start that Instagram account for your pet, make new music&ndash;better late than never!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/eQYsA1kEKkGvbgfK1bCRWyw4SRc8v5vDLCvZw5l6.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Help those in need.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Even if you can&rsquo;t go out and extend a hand to those in need right now, there are ways to help! Reach out to organizations putting together donations for supplies if you can, stay tuned to the news for updates on areas and industries that need the most assistance, and try to uplift those around you with positivity and words of encouragement!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There&rsquo;s plenty to keep you busy in the weeks to come! In the meantime, stay safe and healthy. We&rsquo;ll see you soon!</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9985","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"discovery-eats-where-to-wine-and-dine-in-manila","title":"Discovery Eats: Where to Wine and Dine in Manila","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/WhkjHXZcX4IniKWO7ES34y6KMx5lbK-metaRFMgRm9vZCA3LmpwZw%3D%3D-.jpg","image":null,"description":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Through the years, Manila has become a sought-after foodie destination with its diverse culinary scene. From burgeoning food parks, well-loved neighborhood restos, and international franchises, dining in the pulsating city makes hungry diners spoilt for choice.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;re a discerning food and wine connoisseur and enjoy the finer things in life, then read further to find out more about the culinary gems of Discovery, located just around the metro.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>22 Prime in Discovery Suites</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Fancy a steak-cation? In the middle of bustling Ortigas is Discovery Suites, home to the meat lovers&rsquo; mecca 22 Prime. From the hotel lobby, simply take the elevator to the 22nd floor for a panoramic view of the city, an extensive wine selection, plus the friendliest waiters in town.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;re not sure on what to order, Executive Chef Gerwin Bailon recommends the juicy and fall-off-the-bone USDA Prime Tomahawk, paired with a bottle of Dado Cabernet Sauvignon, a fruity dark red wine with a hint of toasty vanilla.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/NOOoRlPWCqkZEQ4BlLaKpY0VqoIC8gfn9ef1NcUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"689\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">DINING TIP: Watch out for the limited 1-800 PRIME events! P1,800 per person for <a href=\"../../../../dining/22-prime/\">unlimited steak</a>, sides, dessert, and a glass of wine, all for a good cause. Be sure to check Discovery Suites on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter for updates on the next event! Partner beneficiary is an Aeta community in Tarlac through international NGO Waves for Water. Read more about it <a href=\"../../../../about-us/advocacies/\">here</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>22 Prime is open daily from 11:00 AM to 11:00 PM.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button medium\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; text-wrap: nowrap; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoverysuites.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Restaurant Tapenade in Discovery Primea</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;re craving for the tempting flavors of the Mediterranean, from Spain, Italy, France, Greece, Turkey and Morocco, Restaurant Tapenade should be your top-of-mind dining destination.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Famed for its bestselling Salad Room, hungry diners can expect an abundant spread of freshly-harvested greens, dressings and vinaigrettes, as well as flavored-oils, dips and salsas, cheese, charcuterie and fresh seafood.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/D83KAGQWm8a0WrAomUnjWTxtEh3a9wNNqM4AELE0.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"790\" height=\"526\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Definitely try the Porcini-Crusted Ribeye for a meal fit for a king. The porcini&rsquo;s umami flavor gives a mouthwatering kick to the tender meat, topped with flavorful arugula and shaved parmesan for an unforgettable dish. Pair it with Beringer Knights Valley Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon, the best accompaniment to a good ol&rsquo; steak.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Discover Makati&rsquo;s <a href=\"../../../../dining/best-restaurant-makati/\">best Mediterranean restaurant</a>. Restaurant Tapenade is open daily from 6:00 AM to 11:00 PM.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-size: 14.9691px; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button medium\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; text-wrap: nowrap; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>F</strong><strong>lame Restaurant in Discovery Primea</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Waiting for you on the 16th floor of Makati&rsquo;s premier skyscraper are commanding views of the metro, an unobtrusive culinary team, and a live chandelier that&rsquo;s good-on-gram. For an elevated dining experience, Flame Restaurant is the place to go. Delight in the epicurean flavors of<a href=\"../../../../dining/flame-restaurant/\"> modern Asian cuisine</a>, the latest adaptation of Flame&rsquo;s ever-evolving menu.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Looking for the Chef&rsquo;s Recommendation? Executive Chef Luis Chikiamco swears by the Foie Gras Chawanmushi, a delectable Japanese egg custard appetizer available on the a la carte lunch menu. This is best paired with a glass of Ferrari Carano Fume Blanc, which is bursting with flavors of pink grapefruit, lemongrass, honeydew melon, guava, and orange blossom &ndash; the perfect match for ethnic Asian cuisine.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/bV41lCxG8bfSt1wZszD8vrM3B7VgYTL6NZqNND4G.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"790\" height=\"527\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">SOCIAL MEDIA TIP: Flame&rsquo;s dishes are certified-Instagrammable. Get your Boomerang ready for the flaming Baked Alaska dessert, which comes with strawberry and pistachio ice cream, mixed berry compote and triple sec alcohol &ndash; a fiery way to conclude a memorable meal. Use the hashtags #FlameRestaurantPH #DiscoveryPrimea #MakatiSkyline.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Flame is open Mondays to Saturdays from 11:30 AM to 2:30 PM, and from 6 PM to 10 PM.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-size: 14.9691px; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button medium\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; text-wrap: nowrap; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2023-01-06T16:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blog/where-to-wine-and-dine-in-manila","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-05-07T08:43:44.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-09-17T07:58:17.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"5849","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"WhkjHXZcX4IniKWO7ES34y6KMx5lbK-metaRFMgRm9vZCA3LmpwZw==-.jpg","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"5850","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"5851","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Through the years, Manila has become a sought-after foodie destination with its diverse culinary scene. From burgeoning food parks, well-loved neighborhood restos, and international franchises, dining in the pulsating city makes hungry diners spoilt for choice.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;re a discerning food and wine connoisseur and enjoy the finer things in life, then read further to find out more about the culinary gems of Discovery, located just around the metro.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>22 Prime in Discovery Suites</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Fancy a steak-cation? In the middle of bustling Ortigas is Discovery Suites, home to the meat lovers&rsquo; mecca 22 Prime. From the hotel lobby, simply take the elevator to the 22nd floor for a panoramic view of the city, an extensive wine selection, plus the friendliest waiters in town.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;re not sure on what to order, Executive Chef Gerwin Bailon recommends the juicy and fall-off-the-bone USDA Prime Tomahawk, paired with a bottle of Dado Cabernet Sauvignon, a fruity dark red wine with a hint of toasty vanilla.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/NOOoRlPWCqkZEQ4BlLaKpY0VqoIC8gfn9ef1NcUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"689\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">DINING TIP: Watch out for the limited 1-800 PRIME events! P1,800 per person for <a href=\"../../../../dining/22-prime/\">unlimited steak</a>, sides, dessert, and a glass of wine, all for a good cause. Be sure to check Discovery Suites on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter for updates on the next event! Partner beneficiary is an Aeta community in Tarlac through international NGO Waves for Water. Read more about it <a href=\"../../../../about-us/advocacies/\">here</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>22 Prime is open daily from 11:00 AM to 11:00 PM.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button medium\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; text-wrap: nowrap; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoverysuites.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Restaurant Tapenade in Discovery Primea</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you&rsquo;re craving for the tempting flavors of the Mediterranean, from Spain, Italy, France, Greece, Turkey and Morocco, Restaurant Tapenade should be your top-of-mind dining destination.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Famed for its bestselling Salad Room, hungry diners can expect an abundant spread of freshly-harvested greens, dressings and vinaigrettes, as well as flavored-oils, dips and salsas, cheese, charcuterie and fresh seafood.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/D83KAGQWm8a0WrAomUnjWTxtEh3a9wNNqM4AELE0.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"790\" height=\"526\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Definitely try the Porcini-Crusted Ribeye for a meal fit for a king. The porcini&rsquo;s umami flavor gives a mouthwatering kick to the tender meat, topped with flavorful arugula and shaved parmesan for an unforgettable dish. Pair it with Beringer Knights Valley Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon, the best accompaniment to a good ol&rsquo; steak.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Discover Makati&rsquo;s <a href=\"../../../../dining/best-restaurant-makati/\">best Mediterranean restaurant</a>. Restaurant Tapenade is open daily from 6:00 AM to 11:00 PM.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-size: 14.9691px; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button medium\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; text-wrap: nowrap; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>F</strong><strong>lame Restaurant in Discovery Primea</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Waiting for you on the 16th floor of Makati&rsquo;s premier skyscraper are commanding views of the metro, an unobtrusive culinary team, and a live chandelier that&rsquo;s good-on-gram. For an elevated dining experience, Flame Restaurant is the place to go. Delight in the epicurean flavors of<a href=\"../../../../dining/flame-restaurant/\"> modern Asian cuisine</a>, the latest adaptation of Flame&rsquo;s ever-evolving menu.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Looking for the Chef&rsquo;s Recommendation? Executive Chef Luis Chikiamco swears by the Foie Gras Chawanmushi, a delectable Japanese egg custard appetizer available on the a la carte lunch menu. This is best paired with a glass of Ferrari Carano Fume Blanc, which is bursting with flavors of pink grapefruit, lemongrass, honeydew melon, guava, and orange blossom &ndash; the perfect match for ethnic Asian cuisine.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/bV41lCxG8bfSt1wZszD8vrM3B7VgYTL6NZqNND4G.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"790\" height=\"527\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">SOCIAL MEDIA TIP: Flame&rsquo;s dishes are certified-Instagrammable. Get your Boomerang ready for the flaming Baked Alaska dessert, which comes with strawberry and pistachio ice cream, mixed berry compote and triple sec alcohol &ndash; a fiery way to conclude a memorable meal. Use the hashtags #FlameRestaurantPH #DiscoveryPrimea #MakatiSkyline.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Flame is open Mondays to Saturdays from 11:30 AM to 2:30 PM, and from 6 PM to 10 PM.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-size: 14.9691px; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button medium\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; text-wrap: nowrap; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9962","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.featured_