inter; margin: 0px; border-radius: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 0.7778rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-width: 0px 0px 3px; border-image: initial; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) 0s; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: #9c8a5c !important; border-color: initial initial rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\" href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com/restaurant-bar-inquiry/\">BOOK A TABLE</a></p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9965","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"the-self-care-journey-wellness-centers-in-the-philippines","title":"The Self-Care Journey: Wellness Centers in the Philippines","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/F1AswOB2F1MELzChpcSqY51YVtsE3p-metaRmViLTIwMjQtVGhlLWltcG9ydGFuY2Utb2Ytc2VsZi1jYXJlLnBuZw%3D%3D-.png","image":["0e3fe667-707b-4336-adc7-d375702e1ad0"],"description":"<p>In a world where hustle and bustle culture has become part of the norm, it pays to be extra mindful of looking after one&rsquo;s well-being through the art of self-care.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>The importance of self-care</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/ahuLexrwIECk3lQHuplCfqosHHQtrb3D2hljReTV.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The concept of self-care has significantly evolved over the years, where it&rsquo;s no longer viewed as mere luxurious indulgence but also as an important aspect of one&rsquo;s holistic lifestyle.</p>\n<p>In the Philippines, there is already a growing awareness when it comes to practicing self-care. It allows us to look after our mental, emotional, and physical well-being, which are all essential as we go about our daily lives.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Are you looking to disconnect and unwind for a much-needed breather from your daily hustle? Take a deep breath as we walk you through our curated list of wellness center destinations in the Philippines.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Boracay</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/kgu3jKlIxcqc0XrfAnlXL44IDco8GZuPzC8HsUre.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Boracay Island</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Beyond its famous clear water and fine white sand beach, Boracay Island offers some of the best wellness center spots. Escape to this relaxing slice of paradise as you embark on a transformative journey, offering rejuvenation and nourishment of the mind, body, and soul.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/uxz3PTrKLbp4V4i7rm7rEBJmhlFHxNnOiXXS7HUs.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Signature Oils at Terra Wellness Spa at Discovery Boracay (known as Discovery Shores Boracay)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Looking to connect with and be one with nature amid this tropical island paradise? From <a href=\"https://www.discoveryshoresboracay.com/wellness-recreation/best-spa-in-boracay/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">traditional Filipino therapy</a> to specialized treatments, Terra Wellness Spa at Discovery Boracay will take you on a journey to tranquility and serenity as you reconnect in a sanctuary designed to help you float back to reality at your own pace.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Coron</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/rGvs6Uw2JzZEqJbpkRxFEItv4bABC80cOsLEkYwM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Dimakya Island in Coron, Palawan</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">How about a transformative experience tucked away in the pristine natural beauty of Coron, Palawan? Situated far away from the fast-paced nature of urban life, Coron carves out a safe sanctuary where you can rekindle the harmony of the mind, body, and spirit.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/p291zVMExo7VTi2NjwSZ5WTeh5gyKngfTTFB2Ina.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">The use of 100% coconut oil at Glow Spa at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Hailing in an exclusive island paradise is Discovery Coron&rsquo;s very own Glow Spa. Get immersed in an <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/recreation/coron-spa/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">all-natural spa treatment</a> using 100% coconut oil, that will not only soothe your senses but also protect the environment. The resort spa&rsquo;s partnership with Above Aesthetic Clinic (AAC) pushes for the development of detoxification and rejuvenating treatments that combine Oriental and Western techniques.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Sipalay, Negros Occidental</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/WgRCdmb5NopIthQ9nzeW9VEPW1wakGZz6WMOjS9l.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"668\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Sipalay, Negros Occidental&rsquo;s coastal view</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Imagine waking up to the soothing sound of waves at a charming coastal destination like Sipalay, Negros Occidental. Amid picturesque landscapes, the island is an ideal sanctuary for those seeking solace and rejuvenation. Sipalay&rsquo;s rich culture and warm hospitality can turn your getaway into an immersive journey toward finding inner balance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/uy6VePHesPeJBOqp8YTPuOhNSc102Mc08o2KU2ns.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">A secluded spot at Linong Spa at Manami Resort</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Known as a Sanctuary to the Senses, Linong Spa at Manami Resort is a state-of-the-art healing ground, offering the best fusion of nature&rsquo;s healing magic and the genuine care of the human touch. This <a href=\"https://www.manamiresort.com/things-to-do-sipalay/linong-spa/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">luxury wellness center</a> in Sipalay, Negros Occidental, offers an ultimate sensory experience, where you can enjoy the views of the resort while getting lost in the rhythms of nature sounds and the soothing aroma of signature oils for a relaxed mind.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Makati</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0G6gb0K5fCFqIVSisC8TnGRPQKRfbRhYqGZQluZD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Ayala Triangle Park at night in Makati City</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Amidst tall skyscrapers and the energetic pulse of the city, Makati City boasts hidden sanctuaries that provide an oasis of calm, one where you can soothe and recharge your senses.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0IjdhI7QIszPYsSSsBjX3nrQcNzNNQVCXBxZxQl9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Hammam Treatment at Terazi Spa at Discovery Primea</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Among them is Terazi Spa at Discovery Primea, where a haven of understated elegance and unparalleled wellness services await you. Indulge in a selection of traditional and natural healing therapies. A Terazi Spa signature is the <a href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com/wellness-recreation/turkish-spa-manila/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">Turkish Bath</a> or Hammam treatment, which makes use of meticulously sourced ingredients that are crafted to harmonize and rejuvenate the body and soul.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Now that you know some of the wellness center hotspots in the Philippines, where do you see yourself going first?</p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2024-01-08T16:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blog/the-self-care-journey-wellness-centers-in-the-philippines","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-06-14T09:26:28.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-10-01T03:39:51.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"6942","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"F1AswOB2F1MELzChpcSqY51YVtsE3p-metaRmViLTIwMjQtVGhlLWltcG9ydGFuY2Utb2Ytc2VsZi1jYXJlLnBuZw==-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"6943","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"[\"0e3fe667-707b-4336-adc7-d375702e1ad0\"]","state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[{"id":"720","type":"media","attributes":{"uuid":"0e3fe667-707b-4336-adc7-d375702e1ad0","collection_name":"blueprint_media","file_name":"Wn5677mYT7l9p5qnVWGCvPogCLoW2E-metaRmViLTIwMjQtVGhlLWltcG9ydGFuY2Utb2Ytc2VsZi1jYXJlLnBuZw==-.png","custom_properties":[],"original_url":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/720/Wn5677mYT7l9p5qnVWGCvPogCLoW2E-metaRmViLTIwMjQtVGhlLWltcG9ydGFuY2Utb2Ytc2VsZi1jYXJlLnBu