g 100% coconut oil, that will not only soothe your senses but also protect the environment. The resort spa&rsquo;s partnership with Above Aesthetic Clinic (AAC) pushes for the development of detoxification and rejuvenating treatments that combine Oriental and Western techniques.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Sipalay, Negros Occidental</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/WgRCdmb5NopIthQ9nzeW9VEPW1wakGZz6WMOjS9l.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"668\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Sipalay, Negros Occidental&rsquo;s coastal view</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Imagine waking up to the soothing sound of waves at a charming coastal destination like Sipalay, Negros Occidental. Amid picturesque landscapes, the island is an ideal sanctuary for those seeking solace and rejuvenation. Sipalay&rsquo;s rich culture and warm hospitality can turn your getaway into an immersive journey toward finding inner balance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/uy6VePHesPeJBOqp8YTPuOhNSc102Mc08o2KU2ns.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">A secluded spot at Linong Spa at Manami Resort</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Known as a Sanctuary to the Senses, Linong Spa at Manami Resort is a state-of-the-art healing ground, offering the best fusion of nature&rsquo;s healing magic and the genuine care of the human touch. The wellness center offers an ultimate sensory experience, where you can enjoy the views of the resort while getting lost in the rhythms of nature sounds and the soothing aroma of signature oils for a relaxed mind.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Makati</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0G6gb0K5fCFqIVSisC8TnGRPQKRfbRhYqGZQluZD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Ayala Triangle Park at night in Makati City</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Amidst tall skyscrapers and the energetic pulse of the city, Makati City boasts hidden sanctuaries that provide an oasis of calm, one where you can soothe and recharge your senses.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0IjdhI7QIszPYsSSsBjX3nrQcNzNNQVCXBxZxQl9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Hammam Treatment at Terazi Spa at Discovery Primea</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Among them is Terazi Spa at Discovery Primea, where a haven of understated elegance and unparalleled wellness services await you. Indulge in a selection of traditional and natural healing therapies. A Terazi Spa signature is the Turkish Bath or Hammam treatment, which makes use of meticulously sourced ingredients that are crafted to harmonize and rejuvenate the body and soul.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Now that you know some of the wellness center hotspots in the Philippines, where do you see yourself going first?</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"9961","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"a-closer-look-on-sustainable-tourism","title":"A Closer Look on Sustainable Tourism","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Ztb1jrQragBfFJu5gyymurAeDbdoX2-metaTWFyIDIwMjQgLSBJbnRyb2R1Y3Rpb24gLnBuZw%3D%3D-.png","image":["8fddac89-e1ca-4b1f-aa69-33212a4301e3"],"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In a changing world where the global community grapples with the urgent need for environmental preservation, sustainable tourism takes center stage now more than ever. Often referred to as the conscientious approach to a traveling lifestyle, the initiative seeks to reduce the overall negative impacts of tourism on the environment and local communities.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0744c2ef-7fff-a684-c465-94befd8445b6\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Let us take a closer look at how sustainable tourism is beyond just a trend; rather, it can be a transformative approach that will redefine the world of travel and exploration.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-acb0a62e-7fff-2ab2-e18f-eda0a16165e7\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">What is sustainable tourism?</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/h3eWxczUtExSrhseQbsjEp9VVdMXfESTx38Ey48h.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">According to the definition of the United Nations World Tourism Organization (UNWTO), sustainable tourism is &ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">tourism that takes full account of its current and future economic, social, and environmental impacts, addressing the needs of visitors, the industry, the environment, and host communities.</span><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">It is a forward-thinking approach that seeks to balance the enjoyment and exploration of destinations with the desire to protect and preserve them for future generations. Having a deep understanding of sustainable tourism is essential to safeguarding our planet and its diverse communities.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-43a8fdc0-7fff-b751-7b8c-2431a89f81aa\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Let&rsquo;s take a closer look at its importance and how it benefits both travelers and destinations alike. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a2b1665f-7fff-b637-5deb-1152f6f5641b\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">The importance of sustainable tourism</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Sxckbkrqa90ir4Xn4H8GJAleFahpVWPysKQfT83q.png\" alt=\"A demonstration of local and sustainable craftsmanship at Sipalay, Negros Occidental\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2e2ffe4a-7fff-2e0e-428d-6671fc4ac159\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">A demonstration of local and sustainable craftsmanship at Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></span></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-cfb8708d-7fff-92ec-36e6-d06a10b4dafd\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Environmental Protection</span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ead586a-7fff-0c43-5c96-8135c53c7266\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Natural landscapes, wildlife, and a well-balanced ecosystem contribute to what makes destinations unique and breathtaking. Without sustainable practices in place, it can endanger the natural beauty and biodiversity of the destination. </span></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b208a786-7fff-6cb2-38b9-d335d11187ca\"><span style=\"color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cultural Preservation </span></span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bc8cfe6c-7fff-d473-730f-cb9c48181067\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Fostering cultural preservation allows travelers to experience and appreciate the heritage and traditions of the destinations they visit. Sustainable practices minimize the negative impacts of tourism, ensuring the preservation of tourist spots and their vibrancy for future generations.</span></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b208a786-7fff-6cb2-38b9-d335d11187ca\"><span style=\"color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Enhanced Travel Experiences</span></span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ec2f5f4-7fff-06bf-ff15-dfa8a4cd96fe\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">More authentic and enriching travel experiences will await travelers. Through responsible engagement with the local community, tourists can gain deeper insights and create lasting memories while being aware of the positive contributions they have brought to the locale. </span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f652e0-7fff-39ff-07b6-51b2aaa633e2\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">How to practice sustainable tourism</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">By adopting mindful and <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/about-us/advocacies\">eco-friendly practices</a>, your travel memories will not only be memorable but also impactful and extra meaningful. Together, let us explore the practical steps on how you can make a difference through the practice of sustainable tourism.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-17c41eab-7fff-ae86-3014-5367d32a0a5f\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Minimize Waste and Consumption</span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Waste and consumption are at the forefront of pressing environmental issues. By making conscious choices in our everyday lives, we make a collective contribution to a healthier planet, securing a more sustainable future ahead.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Here&rsquo;s one example.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/SsOnaq2DjMdYNrH2d0ngp7d52YtLXghFkKYhdDa7.png\" alt=\"A beach clean-up initiative at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c54dc398-7fff-a176-bcab-b3dbda93aca5\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">A beach clean-up initiative at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1b1fc36b-7fff-b84e-5496-686254f3944c\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Discovery Coron, known as Club Paradise Palawan, is one of the Philippines&rsquo; well-loved tropical paradise destinations, popular for its stunningly remote location along the UNESCO Biosphere Reserve. Although abundant in the finest of nature&rsquo;s resources, one of the challenges that the resort has faced is the lack of regular waste collection. </span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/OaXlLxeAKFiBmdCBv0LDON8cC6dfhk57RWQXAFZv.png\" alt=\"Discovery Coron&rsquo;s EcoConserve Program: Transforming waste into wonderful\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-123f86d3-7fff-8152-a0ef-a52bc22b27ce\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">Discovery Coron&rsquo;s EcoConserve Program: Transforming waste into wonderful</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">To address this, the resort launched the <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/plastic-bottle-to-ecobrick/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">EcoConserve Program</a>, a collective effort to transform waste into something beautiful and functional. For instance, empty wine bottles are repurposed as vase decorations in the restaurant, and driftwood washed ashore is turned into unique chairs.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0Ime196HMn7UhmppaVQhxYn9iIBG1K5ONBBJ1JRJ.png\" alt=\"The EcoConserve project highlights the campaign to phase out Single-Use Plastics (SUPs)\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ca267e8-7fff-604a-cad3-49ca10831ba0\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">The EcoConserve project highlights the campaign to phase out Single-Use Plastics (SUPs)</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-758a4c32-7fff-055d-a65d-9725d947fdbd\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">The resort has also joined the campaign to phase out single-use plastic to address the growing concern over plastic waste. Instead of plastic mineral bottles, EcoPure water bottles are available in the rooms. Guests can enjoy sipping their beverages with sugarcane straws, instead of plastic ones. Laundry bags have also made the switch from plastic to recyclable fabric.</span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/xYrlq0l2PdeduKj4MhrQp1c43LjMpRV5OkkO6xkl.png\" alt=\"Turtle Hatchlings for release at Discovery Coron\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b0571866-7fff-c031-411c-ceff6853f9d6\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Turtle Hatchlings for release at Discovery Coron</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The shores also serve as a Turtle Nesting Site for Hawkbill Sea Turtles and Sea Green Turtles every year, where approximately 200 hatchlings are released back into the ocean.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-00a945a0-7fff-2c50-abf7-a8695c7a05f5\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br /><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">These are only some of the resort&rsquo;s notable initiatives. To learn more, you can visit Discovery Coron&rsquo;s </span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/discover/advocacies/\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #1155cc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">website</span></a><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">. </span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-17c41eab-7fff-ae86-3014-5367d32a0a5f\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choosing Eco-Friendly Accommodations</span></span></strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/edP8ioaxTvM4G3FHYNvgzSRZvMbAhDWfJmK9brUg.png\" alt=\"Discovery Coron: A sustainable tropical paradise in Palawan\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-19dc2c89-7fff-cc0f-5573-c65ff3cef039\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Discovery Coron: A sustainable tropical paradise in Palawan</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choosing destinations that prioritize sustainability makes room for a reduced carbon footprint and supports conservation efforts. What sets <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/select-by-hotel\">eco-friendly hotels</a> apart from traditional accommodations is their commitment to environmental stewardship and sustainable practices. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/lVOTv8tYIPmB8R98X1MhIIU7OrbCM3vvdZlfvHFf.png\" alt=\"Manami Resort: A forerunner in eco-friendly tourism in Sipalay, Negros Occidental\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6b1f3fc8-7fff-16b6-e6c8-46f5a6523f16\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">Manami Resort: A forerunner in eco-friendly tourism in Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Boasting its natural resources and stunning landscapes, the Philippines is an ideal destination for eco-conscious travelers. Accommodations like Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan) and Manami Resort showcase this commitment with their sustainable practices and initiatives. From <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/sustainable-farming-in-coron-palawan/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">farm-to-table practices</a> to the preservation of the local culture, these steps, no matter how small, create a big impact on the environment and the community.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-20b64746-7fff-4471-8f97-b182a8331f7c\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">By prioritizing sustainable tourism, you contribute to preserving our home planet and ensuring that future generations can enjoy the same breathtaking experiences. </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-80f35d53-7fff-ce1d-af67-00efb26ad95e\"></span></p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2024-03-14T16:10:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blogs/a-closer-look-on-sustainable-tourism","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-07-29T01:51:38.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-10-01T04:09:33.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"10765","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"Ztb1jrQragBfFJu5gyymurAeDbdoX2-metaTWFyIDIwMjQgLSBJbnRyb2R1Y3Rpb24gLnBuZw==-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"10766","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"[\"8fddac89-e1ca-4b1f-aa69-33212a4301e3\"]","state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[{"id":"855","type":"media","attributes":{"uuid":"8fddac89-e1ca-4b1f-aa69-33212a4301e3","collection_name":"blueprint_media","file_name":"63MEFnzDYgCqSpO0k3k677fKJf46rd-metaTWFyIDIwMjQgLSBJbnRyb2R1Y3Rpb24gLnBuZw==-.png","custom_properties":[],"original_url":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/855/63MEFnzDYgCqSpO0k3k677fKJf46rd-metaTWFyIDIwMjQgLSBJbnRyb2R1Y3Rpb24gLnBuZw%3D%3D-.png","generated_conversions":[],"type":"image"}}]}},{"id":"10767","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In a changing world where the global community grapples with the urgent need for environmental preservation, sustainable tourism takes center stage now more than ever. Often referred to as the conscientious approach to a traveling lifestyle, the initiative seeks to reduce the overall negative impacts of tourism on the environment and local communities.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0744c2ef-7fff-a684-c465-94befd8445b6\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Let us take a closer look at how sustainable tourism is beyond just a trend; rather, it can be a transformative approach that will redefine the world of travel and exploration.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-acb0a62e-7fff-2ab2-e18f-eda0a16165e7\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">What is sustainable tourism?</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/h3eWxczUtExSrhseQbsjEp9VVdMXfESTx38Ey48h.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">According to the definition of the United Nations World Tourism Organization (UNWTO), sustainable tourism is &ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">tourism that takes full account of its current and future economic, social, and environmental impacts, addressing the needs of visitors, the industry, the environment, and host communities.</span><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">It is a forward-thinking approach that seeks to balance the enjoyment and exploration of destinations with the desire to protect and preserve them for future generations. Having a deep understanding of sustainable tourism is essential to safeguarding our planet and its diverse communities.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-43a8fdc0-7fff-b751-7b8c-2431a89f81aa\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Let&rsquo;s take a closer look at its importance and how it benefits both travelers and destinations alike. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a2b1665f-7fff-b637-5deb-1152f6f5641b\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">The importance of sustainable tourism</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Sxckbkrqa90ir4Xn4H8GJAleFahpVWPysKQfT83q.png\" alt=\"A demonstration of local and sustainable craftsmanship at Sipalay, Negros Occidental\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2e2ffe4a-7fff-2e0e-428d-6671fc4ac159\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">A demonstration of local and sustainable craftsmanship at Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></span></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-cfb8708d-7fff-92ec-36e6-d06a10b4dafd\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Environmental Protection</span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ead586a-7fff-0c43-5c96-8135c53c7266\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Natural landscapes, wildlife, and a well-balanced ecosystem contribute to what makes destinations unique and breathtaking. Without sustainable practices in place, it can endanger the natural beauty and biodiversity of the destination. </span></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b208a786-7fff-6cb2-38b9-d335d11187ca\"><span style=\"color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cultural Preservation </span></span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bc8cfe6c-7fff-d473-730f-cb9c48181067\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Fostering cultural preservation allows travelers to experience and appreciate the heritage and traditions of the destinations they visit. Sustainable practices minimize the negative impacts of tourism, ensuring the preservation of tourist spots and their vibrancy for future generations.</span></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b208a786-7fff-6cb2-38b9-d335d11187ca\"><span style=\"color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Enhanced Travel Experiences</span></span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ec2f5f4-7fff-06bf-ff15-dfa8a4cd96fe\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">More authentic and enriching travel experiences will await travelers. Through responsible engagement with the local community, tourists can gain deeper insights and create lasting memories while being aware of the positive contributions they have brought to the locale. </span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f652e0-7fff-39ff-07b6-51b2aaa633e2\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">How to practice sustainable tourism</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">By adopting mindful and <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/about-us/advocacies\">eco-friendly practices</a>, your travel memories will not only be memorable but also impactful and extra meaningful. Together, let us explore the practical steps on how you can make a difference through the practice of sustainable tourism.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-17c41eab-7fff-ae86-3014-5367d32a0a5f\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Minimize Waste and Consumption</span></span></strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Waste and consumption are at the forefront of pressing environmental issues. By making conscious choices in our everyday lives, we make a collective contribution to a healthier planet, securing a more sustainable future ahead.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Here&rsquo;s one example.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/SsOnaq2DjMdYNrH2d0ngp7d52YtLXghFkKYhdDa7.png\" alt=\"A beach clean-up initiative at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c54dc398-7fff-a176-bcab-b3dbda93aca5\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">A beach clean-up initiative at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1b1fc36b-7fff-b84e-5496-686254f3944c\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Discovery Coron, known as Club Paradise Palawan, is one of the Philippines&rsquo; well-loved tropical paradise destinations, popular for its stunningly remote location along the UNESCO Biosphere Reserve. Although abundant in the finest of nature&rsquo;s resources, one of the challenges that the resort has faced is the lack of regular waste collection. </span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/OaXlLxeAKFiBmdCBv0LDON8cC6dfhk57RWQXAFZv.png\" alt=\"Discovery Coron&rsquo;s EcoConserve Program: Transforming waste into wonderful\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-123f86d3-7fff-8152-a0ef-a52bc22b27ce\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">Discovery Coron&rsquo;s EcoConserve Program: Transforming waste into wonderful</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">To address this, the resort launched the <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/plastic-bottle-to-ecobrick/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">EcoConserve Program</a>, a collective effort to transform waste into something beautiful and functional. For instance, empty wine bottles are repurposed as vase decorations in the restaurant, and driftwood washed ashore is turned into unique chairs.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0Ime196HMn7UhmppaVQhxYn9iIBG1K5ONBBJ1JRJ.png\" alt=\"The EcoConserve project highlights the campaign to phase out Single-Use Plastics (SUPs)\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ca267e8-7fff-604a-cad3-49ca10831ba0\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">The EcoConserve project highlights the campaign to phase out Single-Use Plastics (SUPs)</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-758a4c32-7fff-055d-a65d-9725d947fdbd\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">The resort has also joined the campaign to phase out single-use plastic to address the growing concern over plastic waste. Instead of plastic mineral bottles, EcoPure water bottles are available in the rooms. Guests can enjoy sipping their beverages with sugarcane straws, instead of plastic ones. Laundry bags have also made the switch from plastic to recyclable fabric.</span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/xYrlq0l2PdeduKj4MhrQp1c43LjMpRV5OkkO6xkl.png\" alt=\"Turtle Hatchlings for release at Discovery Coron\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b0571866-7fff-c031-411c-ceff6853f9d6\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Turtle Hatchlings for release at Discovery Coron</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The shores also serve as a Turtle Nesting Site for Hawkbill Sea Turtles and Sea Green Turtles every year, where approximately 200 hatchlings are released back into the ocean.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-00a945a0-7fff-2c50-abf7-a8695c7a05f5\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br /><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">These are only some of the resort&rsquo;s notable initiatives. To learn more, you can visit Discovery Coron&rsquo;s </span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/discover/advocacies/\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #1155cc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">website</span></a><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">. </span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-17c41eab-7fff-ae86-3014-5367d32a0a5f\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choosing Eco-Friendly Accommodations</span></span></strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/edP8ioaxTvM4G3FHYNvgzSRZvMbAhDWfJmK9brUg.png\" alt=\"Discovery Coron: A sustainable tropical paradise in Palawan\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-19dc2c89-7fff-cc0f-5573-c65ff3cef039\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Discovery Coron: A sustainable tropical paradise in Palawan</span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choosing destinations that prioritize sustainability makes room for a reduced carbon footprint and supports conservation efforts. What sets <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/select-by-hotel\">eco-friendly hotels</a> apart from traditional accommodations is their commitment to environmental stewardship and sustainable practices. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/lVOTv8tYIPmB8R98X1MhIIU7OrbCM3vvdZlfvHFf.png\" alt=\"Manami Resort: A forerunner in eco-friendly tourism in Sipalay, Negros Occidental\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6b1f3fc8-7fff-16b6-e6c8-46f5a6523f16\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: super;\">Manami Resort: A forerunner in eco-friendly tourism in Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Boasting its natural resources and stunning landscapes, the Philippines is an ideal destination for eco-conscious travelers. Accommodations like Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan) and Manami Resort showcase this commitment with their sustainable practices and initiatives. From <a href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/sustainable-farming-in-coron-palawan/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">farm-to-table practices</a> to the preservation of the local culture, these steps, no matter how small, create a big impact on the environment and the community.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-20b64746-7fff-4471-8f97-b182a8331f7c\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">By prioritizing sustainable tourism, you contribute to preserving our home planet and ensuring that future generations can enjoy the same breathtaking experiences. </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-80f35d53-7fff-ce1d-af67-00efb26ad95e\"></span></p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"10804","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"Ztb1jrQragBfFJu5gyymurAeDbdoX2-metaTWFyIDIwMjQgLSBJbnRyb2R1Y3Rpb24gLnBuZw==-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"10805","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":["8fddac89-e1ca-4b1f-aa69-33212a4301e3"],"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"10806","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In a changing world where the global community grapples with the urgent need for environmental preservation, sustainable tourism takes center stage now more than ever. Often referred to as the conscientious approach to a traveling lifestyle, the initiative seeks to reduce the overall negative impacts of tourism on the environment and local communities.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0744c2ef-7fff-a684-c465-94befd8445b6\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Let us take a closer look at how sustainable tourism is beyond just a trend; rather, it can be a transformative approach that will redefine the world of travel and exploration.</span></p>\n<h2><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-acb0a62e-7fff-2ab2-e18f-eda0a16165e7\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">What is sustainable tourism?</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/h3eWxczUtExSrhseQbsjEp9VVdMXfESTx38Ey48h.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">According to the definition of the United Nations World Tourism Organization (UNWTO), sustainable tourism is &ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">tourism that takes full account of its current and future economic, social, and environmental impacts, addressing the needs of visitors, the industry, the environment, and host communities.</span><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">It is a forward-thinking approach that seeks to balance the enjoyment and exploration of destinations with the desire to protect and preserve them for future generations. Having a deep understanding of sustainable tourism is essential to safeguarding our planet and its diverse communities.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-43a8fdc0-7fff-b751-7b8c-2431a89f81aa\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Let&rsquo;s take a closer look at its importance and how it benefits both travelers and destinations alike. </span></p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a2b1665f-7fff-b637-5deb-1152f6f5641b\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">The importance of sustainable tourism</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Sxckbkrqa90ir4Xn4H8GJAleFahpVWPysKQfT83q.png\" alt=\"A demonstration of local and sustainable craftsmanship at Sipalay, Negros Occidental\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2e2ffe4a-7fff-2e0e-428d-6671fc4ac159\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">A demonstration of local and sustainable craftsmanship at Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></span></span></p>\n<h3><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-cfb8708d-7fff-92ec-36e6-d06a10b4dafd\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Environmental Protection</span></span></strong></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ead586a-7fff-0c43-5c96-8135c53c7266\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Natural landscapes, wildlife, and a well-balanced ecosystem contribute to what makes destinations unique and breathtaking. Without sustainable practices in place, it can endanger the natural beauty and biodiversity of the destination. </span></span></p>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b208a786-7fff-6cb2-38b9-d335d11187ca\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cultural Preservation </span></span></span></span></strong></h3>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bc8cfe6c-7fff-d473-730f-cb9c48181067\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Fostering cultural preservation allows travelers to experience and appreciate the heritage and traditions of the destinations they visit. Sustainable practices minimize the negative impacts of tourism, ensuring the preservation of tourist spots and their vibrancy for future generations.</span></span></p>\n<p><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a28dcef4-7fff-ec77-14ea-88454e2c14a5\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Enhanced Travel Experiences</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ec2f5f4-7fff-06bf-ff15-dfa8a4cd96fe\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">More authentic and enriching travel experiences will await travelers. Through responsible engagement with the local community, tourists can gain deeper insights and create lasting memories while being aware of the positive contributions they have brought to the locale. </span></span></p>\n<h2><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f652e0-7fff-39ff-07b6-51b2aaa633e2\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">How to practice sustainable tourism</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">By adopting mindful and eco-friendly practices, your travel memories will not only be memorable but also impactful and extra meaningful. Together, let us explore the practical steps on how you can make a difference through the practice of sustainable tourism.</span></p>\n<h3><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-17c41eab-7fff-ae86-3014-5367d32a0a5f\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Minimize Waste and Consumption</span></span></strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Waste and consumption are at the forefront of pressing environmental issues. By making conscious choices in our everyday lives, we make a collective contribution to a healthier planet, securing a more sustainable future ahead.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Here&rsquo;s one example.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/SsOnaq2DjMdYNrH2d0ngp7d52YtLXghFkKYhdDa7.png\" alt=\"A beach clean-up initiative at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c54dc398-7fff-a176-bcab-b3dbda93aca5\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">A beach clean-up initiative at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1b1fc36b-7fff-b84e-5496-686254f3944c\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Discovery Coron, known as Club Paradise Palawan, is one of the Philippines&rsquo; well-loved tropical paradise destinations, popular for its stunningly remote location along the UNESCO Biosphere Reserve. Although abundant in the finest of nature&rsquo;s resources, one of the challenges that the resort has faced is the lack of regular waste collection. </span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/OaXlLxeAKFiBmdCBv0LDON8cC6dfhk57RWQXAFZv.png\" alt=\"Discovery Coron&rsquo;s EcoConserve Program: Transforming waste into wonderful\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-123f86d3-7fff-8152-a0ef-a52bc22b27ce\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Discovery Coron&rsquo;s EcoConserve Program: Transforming waste into wonderful</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">To address this, the resort launched the EcoConserve Program, a collective effort to transform waste into something beautiful and functional. For instance, empty wine bottles are repurposed as vase decorations in the restaurant, and driftwood washed ashore is turned into unique chairs.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/0Ime196HMn7UhmppaVQhxYn9iIBG1K5ONBBJ1JRJ.png\" alt=\"The EcoConserve project highlights the campaign to phase out Single-Use Plastics (SUPs)\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5ca267e8-7fff-604a-cad3-49ca10831ba0\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">The EcoConserve project highlights the campaign to phase out Single-Use Plastics (SUPs)</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-758a4c32-7fff-055d-a65d-9725d947fdbd\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">The resort has also joined the campaign to phase out single plastic to address the growing concern over plastic waste. Instead of plastic mineral bottles, EcoPure water bottles are available in the rooms. Guests can enjoy sipping their beverages with sugarcane straws, instead of plastic ones. Laundry bags have also made the switch from plastic to recyclable fabric.</span></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/xYrlq0l2PdeduKj4MhrQp1c43LjMpRV5OkkO6xkl.png\" alt=\"Turtle Hatchlings for release at Discovery Coron\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b0571866-7fff-c031-411c-ceff6853f9d6\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Turtle Hatchlings for release at Discovery Coron</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The shores also serve as a Turtle Nesting Site for Hawkbill Sea Turtles and Sea Green Turtles every year, where approximately 200 hatchlings are released back into the ocean.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-00a945a0-7fff-2c50-abf7-a8695c7a05f5\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br /><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">These are only some of the resort&rsquo;s notable initiatives. To learn more, you can visit Discovery Coron&rsquo;s </span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.clubparadisepalawan.com/discover/advocacies/\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #1155cc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">website</span></a><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">. </span></span></p>\n<h3><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-17c41eab-7fff-ae86-3014-5367d32a0a5f\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #434343; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choosing Eco-Friendly Accommodations</span></span></strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/edP8ioaxTvM4G3FHYNvgzSRZvMbAhDWfJmK9brUg.png\" alt=\"Discovery Coron: A sustainable tropical paradise in Palawan\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-19dc2c89-7fff-cc0f-5573-c65ff3cef039\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Discovery Coron: A sustainable tropical paradise in Palawan</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Choosing destinations that prioritize sustainability makes room for a reduced carbon footprint and supports conservation efforts. What sets eco-friendly hotels apart from traditional accommodations is their commitment to environmental stewardship and sustainable practices. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/lVOTv8tYIPmB8R98X1MhIIU7OrbCM3vvdZlfvHFf.png\" alt=\"Manami Resort: A forerunner in eco-friendly tourism in Sipalay, Negros Occidental\" width=\"890\" height=\"699\" /></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6b1f3fc8-7fff-16b6-e6c8-46f5a6523f16\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.6em; vertical-align: super;\">Manami Resort: A forerunner in eco-friendly tourism in Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Boasting its natural resources and stunning landscapes, the Philippines is an ideal destination for eco-conscious travelers. Accommodations like Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan) and Manami Resort showcase this commitment with their sustainable practices and initiatives. From farm-to-table practices to the preservation of the local culture, these steps, no matter how small, create a big impact on the environment and the community.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-20b64746-7fff-4471-8f97-b182a8331f7c\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">By prioritizing sustainable tourism, you contribute to preserving our home planet and ensuring that future generations can enjoy the same breathtaking experiences. </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-80f35d53-7fff-ce1d-af67-00efb26ad95e\"></span></p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"10807","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"where-to-next-summer-destinations-in-the-philippines","title":"Where to Next: Summer Destinations in the Philippines","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/k11gPmNVVYh6ksRdYzBL87ENZ2BDJd-metaQXByIDIwMjQgLSBJbnRyb2R1Y3Rpb24ucG5n-.png","image":["682450f7-bbeb-482e-b7f6-beffa1faf39a"],"description":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">As the sun shines brighter and the temperature rises, it&rsquo;s easy to tell that summer is already in the air. The Philippines, best known for its pristine beaches and breathtaking natural landscapes, is undeniably a top summer destination for locals and tourists alike.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">From <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/select-by-location\">award-winning popular destinations</a> such as Palawan and Boracay to hidden idyllic spots on the rise such as Samal, Davao, and Sipalay, Negros Occidental, this tropical paradise offers an array of stunning destinations waiting to be explored.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Join us as we unravel some of the most enticing summer destinations you won&rsquo;t resist adding to your travel bucket list!</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-637e9da5-7fff-b0c0-3904-2aeb85e77a42\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Boracay</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/gU63sTHvPimOwcJFMPDaBgLM19bFGaiguklVpqLL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/9yOEYAqjsx3NuJSMsjpcizGzjjRwax1yaeEjChBD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/b7N89CsjuAnMhuyf2C8KAqNTHHITnfO0mHh3EDnG.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Boracay, a beacon of a beach haven that captivated the hearts of travelers across the globe, is undeniably one of the most popular destinations in the Philippines. Renowned for its powdery white sand and clear turquoise waters, the island serves as a playground for relaxed beach lovers and adventure seekers alike.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Thrill seekers can get their adrenaline fix in a number of water sports, including the likes of parasailing, stand-up paddle boarding, and flyboarding, while those looking for more relaxing activities can shop and dine at the D&rsquo;Mall or sunbathe along the shores. Make sure to stop by Puka Shell Beach too, where you will experience the purity of the island!</span></p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-637e9da5-7fff-b0c0-3904-2aeb85e77a42\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Coron</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/DVoaXW7h9AispLwvX15Ao3ztwxD39hp68I2KfNWV.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/eT63u1ujid22biNx0YCDG7uhZTLa1xaflh7kjvsL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/FO9uIVWNbrwzSOYcewPcbs3z672wwNsiwMBWAPdh.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /></span></span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Often referred to as the last frontier of the Philippines, the untouched beauty of Coron, Palawan, offers a captivating blend of natural wonders and cultural heritage. Popular for its towering limestone cliffs, crystal-clear lagoons, and stunning islands waiting to be explored, this slice of paradise is a stunner to both locals and avid travelers alike.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c495ae57-7fff-7afb-397e-35cdbc7c7403\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Experience the magnificent cleanliness of Kayangan Lake, where you can admire panoramic views before going for a swim or dive, or kayak your way through the Twin Lagoon. Explore shipwrecks in the depths of the island and uncover the secrets of the underwater world brimming with vibrant marine life. </span></p>\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sipalay, Negros Occidental</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/aXD81aq1KjDDyfdEVENWksx6qjbEUbLmikFP907w.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/36q8hDrei0tbPEbYHTGEnYDW11fOZDNF6daQK8IH.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/TfV0UP62xdhKORddp8xONWxXfkXma8QB9DR3WAGQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"199\" height=\"281\" /></span></span></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Thinking of going somewhere off-the-grid? Sipalay, Negros Occidental, may just be the breath of fresh air you&rsquo;re looking for. Known as the &ldquo;Jewel of the Sugar Island,\"&nbsp; Sipalay is an <a href=\"https://www.manamiresort.com/discover/sipalay-city-negros/?utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=webpage&amp;utm_campaign=blog\">emerging beach destination</a> boasting its rich Negrenese heritage, pristine beauty, and laid-back charm.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">What better way to spend your colorful summer days than by exploring the beauty and charm of an uncharted destination? Swim through the famed Tinagong Dagat or Sugar Beach, or dive under the depths of Campomanes Bay.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Island Garden City of Samal, Davao</span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/hQV6t6K3zhTWfeFhDEmDE2wDQYsERsAJdy2QNN80.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/6cQ0VvEtTahzVn1W2dULLsNLGAhLXFP1BodVwMSS.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/f6NdrGiNMTBRGmtoBC11jAy0QTiz6DXyhnCRLO7L.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"198\" height=\"280\" /></span></span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tucked away in the Davao Gulf, the Island Garden City of Samal (or simply Samal Island) may just be your newest summer sanctuary. Vacationers and recreational seekers will be thrilled to explore its untouched beauty and tranquil shores. You can explore and experience its charm through a variety of excursions, including beach hopping, scuba diving, and snorkeling, to name a few.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c92f162a-7fff-7cb1-49ef-809a1ef41ffa\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">It offers unique tourist attractions such as the Monfort Bat Cave, a Guinness World Record holder, housing the largest colony of Rousette fruit bats. The island is also home to the Giant Clam Sanctuary. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-fe579a09-7fff-f310-6397-c540b9c2790f\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">Your next summer destination with Discovery hotels and resorts</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: 