 indoor workouts. Many hotels in the city have fitness centers, or you can try yoga, Pilates, or other exercises in your room. Keeping up with your fitness routine will help you feel energized and healthy during your travels.</p>\n<p><strong>Plan Future Travels</strong>: Spend some time researching and planning your next adventure. Look up <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/special-offers\">vacation packages</a>, create itineraries, and dream about future trips. Use the downtime to gather inspiration and excitement for your next journey.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/select-by-location\">Traveling in the Philippines</a> during the rainy season offers a unique and captivating experience. While the weather may be unpredictable, with a bit of preparation and flexibility, you can still enjoy the stunning landscapes, rich culture, and warm hospitality that the country is known for.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Remember to pack all the right essentials, plan your itinerary with weather conditions in mind, and always prioritize safety. Whether you&rsquo;re navigating the city streets or exploring the crystal-clear waters of its beautiful islands, the Philippines has endless adventures waiting for you.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"12205","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"veZsMjLP8AFho6ulcQuPupBVvGikj4-metabWFuLXRyYXZlbGluZy1pbi10aGUtcmFpbi13aXRoLWx1Z2dhZ2UucG5n-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"12206","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":["9d1001af-0abf-4d5f-8383-53eb1d545009"],"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"12207","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p>The Philippines, with its stunning landscapes and rich cultural heritage, remains a captivating destination year-round. However, traveling during the rainy season, typically from June to November, presents unique challenges and opportunities. Here&rsquo;s everything you need to know to make the most of your trip.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Packing essentials for wet weather</strong></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/iioXxOuWVBEJH2loVgK3DH9PMa2oHqGxlPTppykK.jpg\" alt=\"Packing clothes for a trip\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When traveling in the rainy season, packing the right essentials can make all the difference in your comfort and enjoyment. Here are some must-haves for your trip:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Waterproof Gear: Invest in high-quality waterproof gear, including a durable jacket, rain shoes, and a sturdy umbrella. These items will keep you dry and comfortable as you explore. A waterproof bag is also essential to protect your belongings.</p>\n<p>Insect Repellent: Rainy weather can bring out mosquitoes and other insects. Consider bringing repellent or natural alternatives like citronella oil to protect yourself from bites.</p>\n<p>Portable Charger: Packing a portable charger is essential for any trip, especially during the rainy season when power outages and limited charging opportunities are more likely. Some models include built-in flashlights and additional features which can save space in your luggage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Choosing the right destination</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/xIxB3wPRkfcYRB4eCcNYGWv4eBf5QDdMAxBsrwWK.jpg\" alt=\"Airplane window seat view\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>Selecting the perfect destination for your rainy season travel is crucial. Some places are more enjoyable during wet weather than others. Here are a few tips for choosing the right destination:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Research Rainfall Patterns: Look for destinations with moderate rainfall and fewer chances of severe storms. Some tropical destinations have short, intense showers that quickly clear up, making them ideal for a rainy season visit.</p>\n<p>City Escapes: Urban destinations often have plenty of indoor activities, museums, and cultural sites to explore, making them great choices for rainy days. Districts like Makati and Ortigas offer a plethora of indoor attractions that can keep you entertained regardless of the weather.</p>\n<p>Scenic Beauty: Consider the unique charm of Siargao, where the rain enhances the island's lush scenery and creates ideal surfing conditions. On the other hand, Baguio&rsquo;s cool climate becomes even more refreshing during the rainy season.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Indoor activities to keep you entertained</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/kdn4B2OF6vNIxq08K2nErpfWtxA3Ud369xlSOwUk.jpg\" alt=\"Woman getting a massage\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>Rainy days don&rsquo;t have to be boring. Many destinations offer a variety of indoor activities to keep you entertained throughout your stay:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Museums and Art Galleries: Spend a day exploring local museums and art galleries to soak in the culture and history of your destination. In Makati, the Ayala and Yuchengco Museums offer rich and immersive experiences for all visitors.</p>\n<p>Shopping: Visit local markets and boutiques to discover unique souvenirs and enjoy some retail therapy. Indoor malls like Glorietta and The Podium offer vibrant shopping experiences sheltered from the rain.</p>\n<p>Spa Treatments: Treat yourself to a relaxing spa day. Many resorts and hotels offer luxurious spa services that can help you unwind and recharge. Enjoy massages, facials, and other treatments designed to rejuvenate your body and mind.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Savoring comfort food and cozy meals</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/W3qViYZk0aQJNlOmdVkgeRYhJDlPgNMbgaSmORpp.png\" alt=\"Woman eating a bowl of soup\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>Rainy weather is perfect for indulging in comfort food and cozy meals. Here are some ideas to warm your heart and satisfy your taste buds:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Local Cuisine: Explore the local cuisine and try hearty soups, stews, and other comfort foods that are popular in the region. Enjoy a steaming bowl of bulalo or arroz caldo, which are sure to warm you up.</p>\n<p>Cafes and Bakeries: The soft pattern of raindrops against the window creates a serene atmosphere, perfect for indulging in the comforting flavors of freshly baked treats. Whether you're sharing pastries with friends or enjoying a quiet moment to yourself, a cozy lounge offers a warm respite from the rain.</p>\n<p>Hot Beverages: Warm up with hot beverages like coffee or tea. Seek out unique local variations such as hot tsokolate, a traditional Filipino hot chocolate made from pure cacao tablets and melted into a rich, thick drink.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Making the most of rainy days</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/TkQmOxgwLFoG4X7TnU1yzP3HtUKJhNzNQREw5FXE.png\" alt=\"Woman looking out a hotel room\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>Even when the weather doesn&rsquo;t cooperate, there are plenty of ways to make the most of your rainy days:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Relax and Unwind: Imagine staying at a hotel and sinking into a bed adorned with plush sheets. The room is perfectly chilled, set to just the right temperature to ensure a restful sleep. Everything is within reach, and for those moments when you crave something extra, a simple call to room service is all it takes to bring you what you need.</p>\n<p>Indoor Workouts: Stay active even when it&rsquo;s raining by engaging in indoor workouts. Many hotels have fitness centers, or you can try yoga, Pilates, or other exercises in your room. Keeping up with your fitness routine will help you feel energized and healthy during your travels.</p>\n<p>Plan Future Travels: Spend some time researching and planning your next adventure. Look up destinations, create itineraries, and dream about future trips. Use the downtime to gather inspiration and excitement for your next journey.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Traveling in the Philippines during the rainy season offers a unique and captivating experience. While the weather may be unpredictable, with a bit of preparation and flexibility, you can still enjoy the stunning landscapes, rich culture, and warm hospitality that the country is known for.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Remember to pack all the right essentials, plan your itinerary with weather conditions in mind, and always prioritize safety. Whether you&rsquo;re navigating the city streets or exploring the crystal-clear waters of its beautiful islands, the Philippines has endless adventures waiting for you.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"12208","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"fitness-tips-how-to-stay-active-when-youre-busy","title":"How to Stay Fit and Healthy During Business Trips","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/7HoJw7MiHkUNO0bMb4HozHFdJiOxFQ-metaTWFpbi5wbmc%3D-.png","image":["5eecd8e8-03da-4b00-93dd-a9e68ae798e7"],"description":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Balancing corporate travel and other commitments can make staying fit a challenge&mdash;but with the right approach, you can achieve your goals without compromising your busy lifestyle. Whether you're aiming to lose weight, build muscle, or maintain a healthy routine, this guide offers the best tips for staying on track.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Defining Fitness Goals</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Tl3CIZZ8VCyTkBeulm0ac03mN2Xn6qUJem6Y7fnU.png\" alt=\"Row of dumbbells in the gym.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Setting clear and realistic goals is essential for success. Start by identifying your main goal&mdash;whether it&rsquo;s shedding a few pounds, building muscle, enhancing your endurance, or maintaining overall wellness. Knowing what you want to achieve will help tailor a structured workout schedule that meets your specific needs. Breaking down large goals into manageable steps can also help maintain focus and motivation. If your aim is to run a 10K, start with running a mile and gradually increase your distance each week.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Evaluating Your Lifestyle Needs</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/2ZGZmLSkeCqg1DBWlAmWzKj44StC2ipLDUHKNVhF.png\" alt=\"Young woman checking fitness tracker and phone during a workout break outdoors.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Finding time for fitness is often the biggest challenge for those with demanding schedules, but small adjustments can make a big difference. Assess your daily routine and identify moments that can be dedicated to exercise&mdash;even 20 to 30 minutes of daily physical activity can be impactful. You can also opt for convenient workouts like quick HIIT sessions or short gym visits. Schedule your sessions like any other appointment to build consistency, and add movement throughout your day by taking the stairs, walking during calls, or stretching during breaks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Maximizing Your Gym Experience</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/E1Wpw61bYfM4F6JA9zd4GJ6jOpv0G7n03YWiEF4D.png\" alt=\"Woman lifting a dumbbell in a gym, performing a strength training workout.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In a world where time is precious, your workout sessions must be both efficient and impactful. Choose a gym that is close to your <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/meetings\">business hotel in the city</a>, making it easier to stick to your schedule. Arrive with a well-planned routine, prioritizing exercises such as squats and deadlifts that target multiple muscle groups. Despite a tight schedule, always include warm-ups and cool-downs to prepare your body and aid recovery, helping you maintain peak performance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Prioritizing Health and Wellness</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/N1ZwWD0IelrR0VZCN4hFsgtKIP1kk8wvn0m7TV0b.png\" alt=\"Woman exercising in a hotel gym\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">True fitness extends beyond the gym; it&rsquo;s about embracing a holistic approach to health and wellness. Focus on consuming wholefood, lean proteins, healthy fats, and plenty of fresh fruits and vegetables to nourish your body from the inside out. Staying hydrated is equally important, with at least eight cups of water daily recommended, especially if you engage in high intensity exercise. You can also manage stress through mindful practices like yoga or meditation, cultivating inner calm amidst your demanding schedule.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your journey doesn&rsquo;t have to take a backseat to your busy lifestyle. By embracing this guide, you can elevate your health and well-being, no matter how hectic your schedule gets. As you continue to make small changes, you&rsquo;ll find that maintaining an active routine becomes a natural extension of who you are. Start today and let these tips transform your approach to fitness.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2024-09-05T02:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blogs/how-to-stay-fit-and-healthy-during-business-trips","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-09-05T01:25:54.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-10-01T10:33:58.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"15971","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"7HoJw7MiHkUNO0bMb4HozHFdJiOxFQ-metaTWFpbi5wbmc=-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"15972","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"[\"5eecd8e8-03da-4b00-93dd-a9e68ae798e7\"]","state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[{"id":"947","type":"media","attributes":{"uuid":"5eecd8e8-03da-4b00-93dd-a9e68ae798e7","collection_name":"blueprint_media","file_name":"YhVLuInh2U6sgxuxUYzhGmvSbX14QT-metaTWFpbi5wbmc=-.png","custom_properties":[],"original_url":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/947/YhVLuInh2U6sgxuxUYzhGmvSbX14QT-metaTWFpbi5wbmc%3D-.png","generated_conversions":{"blog_show":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/947/conversions/YhVLuInh2U6sgxuxUYzhGmvSbX14QT-metaTWFpbi5wbmc%3D--blog_show.jpg"},"type":"image"}}]}},{"id":"15973","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Balancing corporate travel and other commitments can make staying fit a challenge&mdash;but with the right approach, you can achieve your goals without compromising your busy lifestyle. Whether you're aiming to lose weight, build muscle, or maintain a healthy routine, this guide offers the best tips for staying on track.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Defining Fitness Goals</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Tl3CIZZ8VCyTkBeulm0ac03mN2Xn6qUJem6Y7fnU.png\" alt=\"Row of dumbbells in the gym.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Setting clear and realistic goals is essential for success. Start by identifying your main goal&mdash;whether it&rsquo;s shedding a few pounds, building muscle, enhancing your endurance, or maintaining overall wellness. Knowing what you want to achieve will help tailor a structured workout schedule that meets your specific needs. Breaking down large goals into manageable steps can also help maintain focus and motivation. If your aim is to run a 10K, start with running a mile and gradually increase your distance each week.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Evaluating Your Lifestyle Needs</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/2ZGZmLSkeCqg1DBWlAmWzKj44StC2ipLDUHKNVhF.png\" alt=\"Young woman checking fitness tracker and phone during a workout break outdoors.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Finding time for fitness is often the biggest challenge for those with demanding schedules, but small adjustments can make a big difference. Assess your daily routine and identify moments that can be dedicated to exercise&mdash;even 20 to 30 minutes of daily physical activity can be impactful. You can also opt for convenient workouts like quick HIIT sessions or short gym visits. Schedule your sessions like any other appointment to build consistency, and add movement throughout your day by taking the stairs, walking during calls, or stretching during breaks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Maximizing Your Gym Experience</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/E1Wpw61bYfM4F6JA9zd4GJ6jOpv0G7n03YWiEF4D.png\" alt=\"Woman lifting a dumbbell in a gym, performing a strength training workout.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In a world where time is precious, your workout sessions must be both efficient and impactful. Choose a gym that is close to your <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/meetings\">business hotel in the city</a>, making it easier to stick to your schedule. Arrive with a well-planned routine, prioritizing exercises such as squats and deadlifts that target multiple muscle groups. Despite a tight schedule, always include warm-ups and cool-downs to prepare your body and aid recovery, helping you maintain peak performance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Prioritizing Health and Wellness</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/N1ZwWD0IelrR0VZCN4hFsgtKIP1kk8wvn0m7TV0b.png\" alt=\"Woman exercising in a hotel gym\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">True fitness extends beyond the gym; it&rsquo;s about embracing a holistic approach to health and wellness. Focus on consuming wholefood, lean proteins, healthy fats, and plenty of fresh fruits and vegetables to nourish your body from the inside out. Staying hydrated is equally important, with at least eight cups of water daily recommended, especially if you engage in high intensity exercise. You can also manage stress through mindful practices like yoga or meditation, cultivating inner calm amidst your demanding schedule.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your journey doesn&rsquo;t have to take a backseat to your busy lifestyle. By embracing this guide, you can elevate your health and well-being, no matter how hectic your schedule gets. As you continue to make small changes, you&rsquo;ll find that maintaining an active routine becomes a natural extension of who you are. Start today and let these tips transform your approach to fitness.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"15974","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"7HoJw7MiHkUNO0bMb4HozHFdJiOxFQ-metaTWFpbi5wbmc=-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"15975","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":["5eecd8e8-03da-4b00-93dd-a9e68ae798e7"],"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"15976","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Balancing work, family, and other commitments can make staying fit a challenge&mdash;but with the right approach, you can achieve your goals without compromising your busy lifestyle. Whether you're aiming to lose weight, build muscle, or maintain a healthy routine, this guide offers the best tips for staying on track.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Defining Fitness Goals</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Tl3CIZZ8VCyTkBeulm0ac03mN2Xn6qUJem6Y7fnU.png\" alt=\"Row of dumbbells in the gym.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Setting clear and realistic goals is essential for success. Start by identifying your main goal&mdash;whether it&rsquo;s shedding a few pounds, building muscle, enhancing your endurance, or maintaining overall wellness. Knowing what you want to achieve will help tailor a structured workout schedule that meets your specific needs. Breaking down large goals into manageable steps can also help maintain focus and motivation. If your aim is to run a 10K, start with running a mile and gradually increase your distance each week.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Evaluating Your Lifestyle Needs</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/2ZGZmLSkeCqg1DBWlAmWzKj44StC2ipLDUHKNVhF.png\" alt=\"Young woman checking fitness tracker and phone during a workout break outdoors.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Finding time for fitness is often the biggest challenge for those with demanding schedules, but small adjustments can make a big difference. Assess your daily routine and identify moments that can be dedicated to exercise&mdash;even 20 to 30 minutes of daily physical activity can be impactful. You can also opt for convenient workouts like quick HIIT sessions or short gym visits. Schedule your sessions like any other appointment to build consistency, and add movement throughout your day by taking the stairs, walking during calls, or stretching during breaks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Maximizing Your Gym Experience</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/E1Wpw61bYfM4F6JA9zd4GJ6jOpv0G7n03YWiEF4D.png\" alt=\"Woman lifting a dumbbell in a gym, performing a strength training workout.\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In a world where time is precious, your gym sessions must be both efficient and impactful. Choose a facility that is close to your home or workplace, making it easier to stick to your schedule. Arrive with a well-planned routine, prioritizing exercises such as squats and deadlifts that target multiple muscle groups. Despite a tight schedule, always include warm-ups and cool-downs to prepare your body and aid recovery, helping you maintain peak performance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Prioritizing Health and Wellness</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/N1ZwWD0IelrR0VZCN4hFsgtKIP1kk8wvn0m7TV0b.png\" alt=\"Woman exercising in a hotel gym\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">True fitness extends beyond the gym; it&rsquo;s about embracing a holistic approach to health and wellness. Focus on consuming wholefood, lean proteins, healthy fats, and plenty of fresh fruits and vegetables to nourish your body from the inside out. Staying hydrated is equally important, with at least eight cups of water daily recommended, especially if you engage in high intensity exercise. You can also manage stress through mindful practices like yoga or meditation, cultivating inner calm amidst your demanding schedule.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your journey doesn&rsquo;t have to take a backseat to your busy lifestyle. By embracing this guide, you can elevate your health and well-being, no matter how hectic your schedule gets. As you continue to make small changes, you&rsquo;ll find that maintaining an active routine becomes a natural extension of who you are. Start today and let these tips transform your approach to fitness.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"15977","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"summer-days-in-the-city-the-benefits-of-a-city-staycation","title":"Summer Days in the City: The Benefits of a City Staycation","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/iZKGzE5wXxXbsCNIHsn82Rw34esbuu-metaREhDIC0gTWF5IDIwMjQgLSBNYWluIEJsb2cgUGhvdG8ucG5n-.png","image":null,"description":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">With the rise in temperature and the cityscape brimming with vibrant energy, there is something uniquely enticing about spending the summer days in the heart of the urban jungle. While jetting off to faraway destinations seems like the norm for a summer getaway, city staycations have their own special charm that can add a unique touch to your summer memories.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The convenience of familiar surroundings brings hidden gems waiting to be discovered. Get ready to see your city in a whole new light as we uncover the perks of a summer staycation in this bustling metropolis.&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><br />Time-efficient and convenient</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/hTHBKGQZHHnQYXUNFoKFtAKa22J1pFiHxLttfi30.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><sup><em>A walkway along Ayala Avenue seamlessly connecting establishments in the area</em></sup></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Without the hassle of long-distance travel, summer city staycations offer the perfect blend of relaxation and adventure. You can explore local attractions, dine at the <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/restaurants\">hottest restaurants</a> in town, or enjoy your hotel amenities. A city staycation lets you recharge without the stress of packing and long journeys.&nbsp; Why not embrace the energetic pulse of the city?</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><br />Discover hidden local gems</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/GMzou252f22Ynyc9CSjxdoQrCSaPGJC0tNvcFq6U.png\" alt=\"\" /></strong><br /><sup><em>An aerial view of Makati City at night</em></sup></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sometimes, the greatest discoveries are closer than we think; all it takes is a little bit of exploration. An escape in the city lets you dive into its distinctive charm&mdash;from the lively streets to the quiet corners where creativity flourishes and every day brings a new adventure!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Take Makati City, for instance. Known for its rich, dynamic lifestyle, Makati offers a diverse range of delights that will make you feel like a local. Uncover unique cafes, restaurants, and bars in quaint neighborhoods, like Poblacion, Legaspi, and Salcedo Villages. Looking to connect with nature while taking a breather? Wander through the leafy pathways of Ayala Triangle Park or enrich your knowledge of Filipino culture at the Ayala Museum.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><br />The perfect balance of exploration and relaxation</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/lZbnyECcqf1xg9bsmTlraQ9cWWHJRSHPcMJcQZua.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><em><sup>Emerald Avenue in Ortigas Center</sup></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine starting your day with a leisurely stroll along the bustling streets of Ortigas Center, lined with modern skyscrapers and bustling with activity. Take delight in the morning buzz as you walk along Emerald Avenue (also known as F. Ortigas Jr. Road). Whether you're in the mood for a hearty breakfast from a fast-food favorite or a smooth latte from a nearby coffee shop, this lively stretch has everything you need to kickstart your day. Along the way, you can look forward to a brief change of scenery when you stop by Ortigas Park, where a touch of nature will keep you company, whether you are winding down after a morning jog or you simply want to take a pause from the daily grind.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Looking to shop the latest trends or maybe catch the latest movie playing with your loved ones? Large malls in the area, such as The Podium and Shangri-La Plaza, provide for all your daily and recreational needs. After an activity-filled day, a cozy hotel like Discovery Suites can provide you the perfect place to relax and recharge before embarking on your next city adventure.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><br />Explore the local metropolitan charm with Discovery Primea and Discovery Suites</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Located in the heart of thriving urban landscapes, Discovery Primea and Discovery Suites bring you the magic of metropolitan charm with unforgettable city sta