f metropolitan charm with unforgettable city stays. Whether you&rsquo;re in town for business or leisure, both of these premier accommodations provide an oasis of comfort amidst the city&rsquo;s dynamic energy, offering easy access to top attractions, dining, and shopping destinations.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/gsM5mw7EGqGbBJCX43EstS8zwyCM0jadDAtvYsPq.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><em><sup>Rooftop infinity pool at Discovery Primea, Makati</sup></em></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">World-class amenities and breathtaking city views in Makati await you at Discovery Primea, where elegantly appointed suite rooms offer a serene escape from the hustle and bustle. Meanwhile, Discovery Suites provides a homey yet deluxe atmosphere in the heart of the Ortigas Center Business District. The spacious suites are ideal for both short and extended stays and are designed to cater to every traveler&rsquo;s needs</span><em>.</em></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Znib9wflRZxG9BXewVoVIryEAgXGaNXrjyfVNARf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"600\" /></span><br /><sup>A guest during a staycation at Discovery Suites, Manila</sup></em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Learn more about Discovery Primea at <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.discoveryprimea.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.discoveryprimea.com</a></span> and Discovery Suites at <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.discoverysuites.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.discoverysuites.com</a></span>&nbsp;</span></p>","state_path":"main.description","type":"tinyeditor"}},{"id":"17527","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.button_links","type":"repeater"}}]},{"type":"contentEntries","id":"city-wedding-or-destination-wedding-the-best-place-to-exchange-your-i-dos","title":"City Wedding or Destination Wedding: The best place to exchange your ‘I dos’","data":{"main":{"featured_image":"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/L2KrdoZxPfmh4CsyqK3KDVIOxrdgHo-metaMi5wbmc%3D-.png","image":null,"description":"<p>When it comes to planning your dream wedding, decision-making plays an essential role. One of the most significant aspects is choosing your perfect location. Whether it&rsquo;s an <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/makati-manila-weddings\">elegant city wedding</a> or a picturesque destination wedding you&rsquo;re dreaming of, it will set the tone for your entire celebration.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Come along as we explore the unique charms and crucial considerations of both city and <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/beach-weddings-philippines\">destination weddings</a>. By the end of this blog, we hope this can help you narrow down your options in choosing your ideal setting for your special day.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>All About City Weddings: Pros and What to consider</strong></h2>\n<p><em><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/TTMxF6QjR3os0UNL8oN97LqXWsSrNGXPVXGxWVGJ.png\" alt=\"\" /></em><br /><sup><em>A couple&rsquo;s photo shoot at Discovery Primea in Makati City</em></sup></p>\n<p><strong>Pros<br /><br /></strong>A perfect blend of glamour and convenience&mdash;ideal for couples seeking a cosmopolitan celebration. City weddings often transpire in iconic venues offering breathtaking cityscape views while providing a picturesque backdrop for photos. Its accessibility to city amenities simplifies logistics for couples and guests alike, providing a wide range of accommodation, dining, and entertainment options.<br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>What to consider</strong><br /><br />Although it does not require long hours of travel, navigating city traffic and parking spaces can pose challenges, as costs may be more expensive due to venue fees and city-specific expenses. Additionally, if you are envisioning a tranquil atomosphere surrounded by nature&rsquo;s beauty, you might find the city&rsquo;s bustling environment and limited green spaces less ideal for the scenic backdrop you have in mind.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>All About Destination Weddings: Pros and What to consider</strong></h2>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/1EsG3SPj4T8NbM0saxwoAUbvyedphdkyPkWDlYDJ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"600\" /></strong><br /><em><sup>An intimate rustic wedding set-up at Discovery Coron (known as Club Paradise Palawan)</sup></em></p>\n<p><strong>Pros</strong></p>\n<p>A picturesque locale far from home, <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/beach-weddings-philippines\">destination weddings</a> bring an exotic and intimate atmosphere for couples looking to tie the knot. Its allure lies in its ability to perfectly mesh the ceremony and honeymoon into an unforgettable, seamless experience. This includes breathtaking settings such as tropical beaches and rustic countryside. Celebrations are more festive, and destination weddings are known to host multiple-day celebrations. This also benefits your guests, as they get to have a mini-vacation, making your special day even more memorable for everyone involved.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br /><strong>What to consider</strong></p>\n<p>Its planning can be more complex, which often requires the assistance of a local wedding planner. Depending on your budget, there may be a travel expense constraint for some guests, which can potentially limit attendance to your closest friends and family.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Which is the better choice?</strong></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/x2xXEOj3SQkXTqTW4bZfnmmI7ejHjyfiAaqUJoEZ.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><em><sup>A picturesque wedding photo shoot at Discovery Boracay</sup></em></p>\n<p>When it comes to making the &ldquo;better choice,\" this all boils down to consideration of certain factors and your personal preferences as a couple. This usually entails your budget and the experience for you and your guests.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Consider answering these questions to help you weigh your options accordingly:</p>\n<p><strong>Preferred Setting</strong>: Are you looking for a posh urban backdrop or a serene and scenic destination?&nbsp;<br /><strong>Budget</strong>: What would best fit your overall budget?<br /><strong>Logistics</strong>: Do you prefer the convenience of planning a wedding in the city or are you up for the complexities of planning a destination wedding?<br /><strong>Guest List</strong>: Do you want it to be a grand celebration with a large number of guests, or do you want a more intimate celebration?<br /><strong>Experience</strong>: What experience do you want to create for yourself and your guests? A chic celebration in the midst of the city&rsquo;s pulsating energy or a dreamy getaway in a faraway destination?</p>\n<p>Both city and destination weddings possess a unique charm of their own. At the end of the day, the better choice is the one that will align with your personal preferences&mdash;vision, priorities, and circumstances.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\n<h2><strong>Celebrate your wedding with Discovery hotels and resorts</strong></h2>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/vqriq61h4rnZ2rIGUb0BzZIUdvCUB4eZayKdCV6I.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"600\" /></strong><br /><em><sup>A beach wedding getaway at Discovery Samal, a five-minute boat ride from Davao City</sup></em></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Located in the Philippines&rsquo; most iconic city and beach destinations, where every moment is designed to be unforgettable, celebrate your wedding with Discovery hotels and resorts.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/as8ntlM90dS5D3w9n8EBdXTpF8pmZeZgqWLfeOT9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"600\" /></span><br /><em><sup>Customized table arrangement at Discovery Suites in Ortigas Center, Pasig City</sup></em></span></p>\n<p>Contemporary yet classic, simple yet sophisticated. Beyond the breathtaking views, highly personalized services are available at Discovery Primea and Discovery Suites, ready to give you that seamless city wedding experience you&rsquo;re envisioning.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/nkTH78AJs9VCiXWeK8fERW7nfqQwiNbU9SAd9cZN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"600\" /><br /><em><sup>Beach wedding at Discovery Coron</sup></em></p>\n<p>Easy, breezy, fun, and memorable&mdash;this is how beach weddings are meant to be. Exchange your sun-kissed I Do&rsquo;s at Discovery Resorts&rsquo; stunning beach destinations in Boracay, Coron, and Samal Island in Davao. Looking to add a flair of unique touches to your celebration? Take your wedding celebration to a distinct sanctuary surrounded by nature&rsquo;s beauty in Sipalay, Negros Occidental&mdash;Manami Resort.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/Zo04qFazhhHNFeJaUFppbXXqER1zq3LtUpSn3wZC.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><em><sup>Couple captured with the sunset at Manami Resort in Sipalay, Negros Occidental (Photo by <a href=\"https://hayagstudios.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">HAYAG Studios</span></a>)<br /></sup></em></p>\n<p>No matter where you dream of saying &lsquo;I do&rsquo;, Discovery hotels and resorts offer a variety of locations to be the perfect setting for your unforgettable celebration.</p>","button_links":null,"gallery_images":null}},"order":null,"published_at":"2024-06-21T02:00:00.000000Z","route_url":"/blogs/city-wedding-or-destination-wedding","locale":"en","created_at":"2024-09-10T09:30:12.000000Z","updated_at":"2024-09-17T09:45:19.000000Z","blueprintData":[{"id":"17528","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"L2KrdoZxPfmh4CsyqK3KDVIOxrdgHo-metaMi5wbmc=-.png","state_path":"main.featured_image","type":"file"}},{"id":"17529","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":null,"state_path":"main.image","type":"media","media":[]}},{"id":"17530","type":"blueprintData","attributes":{"value":"<p>When it comes to planning your dream wedding, decision-making plays an essential role. One of the most significant aspects is choosing your perfect location. Whether it&rsquo;s an <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/makati-manila-weddings\">elegant city wedding</a> or a picturesque destination wedding you&rsquo;re dreaming of, it will set the tone for your entire celebration.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Come along as we explore the unique charms and crucial considerations of both city and <a href=\"https://www.discoveryhotels-resorts.com/meetings-events/beach-weddings-philippines\">destination weddings</a>. By the end of this blog, we hope this can help you narrow down your options in choosing your ideal setting for your special day.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>All About City Weddings: Pros and What to consider</strong></h2>\n<p><em><img src=\"https://haspcms-discovery-suites.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/tinyeditor_uploads/TTMxF6QjR3os0UNL8oN97LqXWsSrNGXPVXGxWVGJ.png\" alt=\"\" /></em><br /><sup><em>A couple&rsquo;s photo shoot at Discovery Primea in Makati City</em></sup></p>\n<p><strong>Pros<br /><br /></strong>A perfect blend of glamour and convenience&mdash;ideal for couples seeking a cosmopolitan celebration. City weddings ofte